NK016(ma)005:0: na rag dong sprugs kyi cho ga 'khor ba kun sgrol zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)005:1: na rag dong sprugs rnal 'byor gyi spyi khrus chen
NK016(ma)005:2: po'i cho ga 'khor ba kun sgrol zhes bya ba
NK016(ma)005:3: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:4: zhi dang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams kyi //
NK016(ma)005:5: khyab bdag dpal ldan bde chen kun tu bzang //
NK016(ma)005:6: bla ma mchog ste rang rig ye shes kyi //
NK016(ma)005:7: ngo bor bzhugs pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:8: ye shes gcig nyid rigs brgya rigs lnga sogs //
NK016(ma)005:9: du ma'i gar gyis srid zhir rgyas 'debs lha'i //
NK016(ma)005:10: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i sgrub thabs rnal 'byor gyi //
NK016(ma)005:11: spyi khrus cho ga 'khor ba kun sgrol bshad //
NK016(ma)005:12: de yang rten gyi gang zag rang dang gzhan gyis
NK016(ma)005:13: bsdus pa'i sems can mtha' yas pa'i sdig sgrib sbyong
NK016(ma)005:14: zhing tshogs gnyis phul du byung ba'i dngos grub 'dod
NK016(ma)005:15: pa dag gis cho ga 'di la 'jug par bya'o
NK016(ma)005:16: // de la thog mar yo byad rnams tshogs par byas nas cho ga la /
NK016(ma)005:22: khyad par gyi sngon 'gro gnyis so //
NK016(ma)005:24: dang po bsang chu sgrub pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:25: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru kar
NK016(ma)005:26: gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las ram yam kham 'phros
NK016(ma)005:27: bas ma dag pa'i dngos 'dzin thams cad bsregs gtor
NK016(ma)005:28: sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las bsang chu'i steng du /
NK016(ma)005:30: nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'u yig dmar po /
NK016(ma)005:34: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:35: khro mo dbang phyug ma dmar po dril bu dang b+han dmar 'dzin pa'i skur gyur par bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)005:36: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas reg la /
NK016(ma)005:37: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai sh+aa ri sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha ya +aahh+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)005:38: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK016(ma)005:39: khro mo dbang phyug ma'i rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsam /
NK016(ma)005:40: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sarba dra b+y+aam shwa d+ha ya h+au phata /
NK016(ma)005:41: ces bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la bsang gtor bya zhing /
NK016(ma)005:42: thogs mtha' kun tu bsang gtor gyi bya ba thams cad 'dis bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:43: gnyis pa gzhi bgegs kyi gtor ma ni /
NK016(ma)005:44: gtor ma dkar dmar rgyan ldan gnyis bshams la bsang sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:45: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+au las rin po che'i snod
NK016(ma)005:46: zab cing rgya che ba'i nang du gtor ma kha
NK016(ma)005:47: dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam
NK016(ma)005:50: s+th+aa na pa ti k+she tra p+aa lany+tsa na mahsarba
NK016(ma)005:51: ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs gsum gyis bsngosa la
NK016(ma)005:52: / gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu //
NK016(ma)005:53: gnod sbyin srin po'am gzhan dag la //
NK016(ma)005:55: bdag zhu khyed kyis stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:58: sarba big+h+n+aam na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs kyis bsngosa la /
NK016(ma)005:61: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK016(ma)005:62: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK016(ma)005:63: thams cad thugs rjes bskangs zin gyi //
NK016(ma)005:64: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK016(ma)005:66: rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK016(ma)005:67: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK016(ma)005:68: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)005:69: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha sogs brjod
NK016(ma)005:70: cing drag po'i tsham rngams dang bcas pas bgegs bskrad
NK016(ma)005:71: de gtor ma phyi rol du dor /
NK016(ma)005:72: gsum pa rten gyi dkyil 'khor 'du bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:73: gang du dkyil 'khor bya ba'i gzhir ba byung gis byugs /
NK016(ma)005:74: dri bzang dang bdud rtsi lngas chag chag btab la /
NK016(ma)005:75: thig skud dri zhim po'i thig chal gyis sbags pa gsar nas /
NK016(ma)005:76: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum du
NK016(ma)005:77: gsal ba snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK016(ma)005:78: thig skud dang ro gcig pa ye shes lnga'i ngo
NK016(ma)005:82: dang por shar nub kyi tshangs thig gdab pa nas
NK016(ma)005:83: bzung thig chen brgyad po dkyil 'khor gyi nam mkha'
NK016(ma)005:84: la gdab cing / de bzhin du sa la yang gdab ste /
NK016(ma)005:86: dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+au tra ma ti kra ma h'u /
NK016(ma)005:88: tshul des gzhal yas khang sgo gnyis sbrags sogs spyi'i
NK016(ma)005:89: khog sgyu 'phrul khro bo dang mthun pa nyid las
NK016(ma)005:90: / lte bar zlum bskor re'u mig dgu pa mu khyud can gyi mthar /
NK016(ma)005:91: rtsibs brgyad pa gnyis rim dang rtsibs bcu drug pa
NK016(ma)005:92: mu khyud dang bcas pas pho brang nang ma'i cha
NK016(ma)005:93: chen bzhi pa'i nang thig tshun bskor pa ni khyad
NK016(ma)005:94: par ro // pho brang nang ma'i khongs su g.yas
NK016(ma)005:95: g.yon du cha chen re re spar nas lha gnas
NK016(ma)005:96: yangs par byed pa yang lag len la snang ngo
NK016(ma)005:97: par ro // // de nas tshon lnga mdog rigs
NK016(ma)005:98: sdebs pa so so'i gnas su h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa
NK016(ma)005:99: par ro // // / m+aum l+aam p+aam m+aam t+aam
NK016(ma)005:100: las de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i ngo bor gyur
NK016(ma)005:101: pa rnams bdag nyid kyi sku la zhugs /
NK016(ma)005:102: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba tshon rtsi rnams la thim par bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)005:103: sa bon bcu po dang +aahsarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h'u h'u /
NK016(ma)005:105: h'u zhes brjod pas rin po che'i rdul phra rab kyi rdul tshon 'bar bar bsam nas /
NK016(ma)005:106: dbus kyi gling dgu'i lte ba mthing ga /
NK016(ma)005:107: phyogs bzhi mtshams thig gis phye ba'i phyogs mdog /
NK016(ma)005:108: gdung bzhi dang mu khyud sngon po /
NK016(ma)005:109: 'khor lo nang nas rim bzhin mthing dmar dkar ba /
NK016(ma)005:111: khyams phyi nang gnyis ka phyogs mdog sogs lhag ma spyi dang mthun par bya zhing /
NK016(ma)005:113: mdog mthun gyi thig le rnams ji ltar rigs pa 'god do //
NK016(ma)005:114: thig tshon gyi las rdzogs pa na ye shes pa mchod nas badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol /
NK016(ma)005:115: de dag ni dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa rnying par
NK016(ma)005:116: skabs 'ga' zhig tu rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub
NK016(ma)005:117: bde ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:118: bzhi pa bum pa bsham pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:119: rnam rgyal bum pa gcig dang /
NK016(ma)005:120: yig brgya'i khrus bum gcig ste /
NK016(ma)005:121: bum pa gnyis po kha rgyan mgul chings nang bcud
NK016(ma)005:122: sogs spyi dang mthun par bshams pa'i rnam rgyal dkyil
NK016(ma)005:124: khrus bum rang gi mdun du bzhag go //
NK016(ma)005:125: lnga pa mchod rdzas bsham pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:126: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha'i nang rim la sman gtor rak+ta
NK016(ma)005:127: mar me ste bskang rdzas rnams brgya yan chad kyi
NK016(ma)005:128: phreng ba dang / de'i phyi rim la bdug spos /
NK016(ma)005:131: dri chab rnams lha grangs dang mnyam pa sogs ji tsam 'byor ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:132: gzhan yang zhabs bsil sogs phyi'i mchod pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)005:133: sman gtor rak+ta la sogs pa nang gi mchod pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)005:136: dar 'phan rgyal mtshan sogs kyis khor yug thams cad du mdzes par brgyan nas /
NK016(ma)005:137: gral phyag dang tshul phyag sngon du 'gro bas stan
NK016(ma)005:138: la 'dug ste rol mos byin dbab ba rnams bya'o
NK016(ma)005:139: // gnyis pa cho ga'i khyad par gyi sngon 'gro la drug gi /
NK016(ma)005:140: dang po rgyud sbyong ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:141: bla ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:142: gyi lha tshogs thams cad badz+ra sa m+aa dzah sa
NK016(ma)005:144: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)005:145: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyal dpal //
NK016(ma)005:146: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:147: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK016(ma)005:148: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)005:149: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:150: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:151: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK016(ma)005:152: nyer byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:153: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK016(ma)005:154: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK016(ma)005:155: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK016(ma)005:156: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)005:157: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK016(ma)005:158: dag pa gsum gyis lus dbul lo //
NK016(ma)005:159: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK016(ma)005:160: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK016(ma)005:161: zhes lan gsum la sogs pas rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:162: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus te chos dbyings ka dag gi klong du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK016(ma)005:163: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:164: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK016(ma)005:165: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru ka
NK016(ma)005:166: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba chen po'i 'od zer
NK016(ma)005:167: can / zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK016(ma)005:168: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK016(ma)005:169: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum pa /
NK016(ma)005:170: sma ra dang smin ma dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu skra gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK016(ma)005:173: g.yon dmar gyis gang ba'i dung chen steng 'og tu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)005:174: sgeg pa la sogs pa'i gar dgu'i nyams kyis rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:175: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang glang po che'i ko bas stod g.yogs shing /
NK016(ma)005:176: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs grol ba /
NK016(ma)005:177: thod pa skam po lnga rigs lnga'i rtse phran can gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK016(ma)005:178: rlon pa lnga bcu'i do shal 'phyang ba /
NK016(ma)005:179: rus pa'i rgyan drug dang sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)005:180: khrag zhag thal ba sogs dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas can /
NK016(ma)005:181: zhabs g.yon bskum zhing g.yas brkyang ba'i dor bstabs kyis dregs pa pho mo mnan pa /
NK016(ma)005:182: yum rdo rje khrag 'thung ma sngon mo gcer bu skra grol zhing lang tshos sgeg pa /
NK016(ma)005:183: g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK016(ma)005:184: g.yon dung dmar stob pa'i tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:185: gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs sogs dur khrod rol
NK016(ma)005:186: pa'i chas can zhabs g.yon brkyang zhing g.yas bskum pas
NK016(ma)005:188: stong pa nyid dang snying rje dbyer med pa'i bdag
NK016(ma)005:189: nyid can ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar pa'i klong
NK016(ma)005:190: na bzhugs pa'o // h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK016(ma)005:191: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK016(ma)005:193: yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol
NK016(ma)005:194: pa mtshon cha sna tshogs kyi char 'bebs pa dpag
NK016(ma)005:196: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK016(ma)005:197: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad zil
NK016(ma)005:198: gyis mnan pas thams cad 'jigs shing skrag nas bag
NK016(ma)005:199: 'khums te gnas par gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)005:203: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)005:205: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK016(ma)005:206: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK016(ma)005:207: h'u h'u phata / ces brjod cing bskul bas /
NK016(ma)005:208: khro bo'i tshogs nam mkha' gang ba rnams kyis gsang
NK016(ma)005:209: spyod blta bar mi dbang ba'i bgegs dang log par
NK016(ma)005:210: 'dren pa thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par byas /
NK016(ma)005:211: badz+ra pany+tsa ra ram yam kham /
NK016(ma)005:213: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK016(ma)005:214: pos gtams pa'i phyi rol kun nas bskal pa'i me
NK016(ma)005:216: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrugs pa'i ra ba gsum rim
NK016(ma)005:217: gyis phyogs kun gang bas mtshams bcad de cis kyang
NK016(ma)005:219: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:220: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs bshags yul rgyal ba zhi khro
NK016(ma)005:221: mkha' khyab tu sad pa'i spyan sngar bshags sdom gyi
NK016(ma)005:224: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK016(ma)005:226: nongs par mchis na rab gnong bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)005:227: zhes pas sdig sgrib thams cad ye nas rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings su dag par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:228: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:229: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya snying gar bcings te lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK016(ma)005:230: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK016(ma)005:231: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK016(ma)005:232: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu pa //
NK016(ma)005:233: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:234: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK016(ma)005:235: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK016(ma)005:236: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK016(ma)005:237: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:238: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK016(ma)005:239: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag sgrub ma lags te //
NK016(ma)005:240: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK016(ma)005:241: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod ni dpang du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:242: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK016(ma)005:243: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK016(ma)005:244: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK016(ma)005:245: sun par mi bgyi mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK016(ma)005:246: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK016(ma)005:247: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK016(ma)005:248: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK016(ma)005:249: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)005:250: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK016(ma)005:251: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK016(ma)005:252: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK016(ma)005:253: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:254: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK016(ma)005:255: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtub kyang //
NK016(ma)005:256: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK016(ma)005:257: yi dam rgyal ba khyod ni yongs mi spangs //
NK016(ma)005:258: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK016(ma)005:259: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK016(ma)005:260: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)005:261: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK016(ma)005:262: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK016(ma)005:263: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK016(ma)005:264: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK016(ma)005:265: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK016(ma)005:266: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK016(ma)005:267: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)005:268: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK016(ma)005:269: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:270: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK016(ma)005:271: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK016(ma)005:272: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK016(ma)005:273: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:274: srid par yun ring dus su brtson pa ni //
NK016(ma)005:275: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pas na //
NK016(ma)005:276: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur pa //
NK016(ma)005:277: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK016(ma)005:278: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK016(ma)005:279: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK016(ma)005:280: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK016(ma)005:281: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:282: 'gro la thugs brtse dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK016(ma)005:283: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK016(ma)005:284: bdag gis 'jig rten thugs pa ma mchis par //
NK016(ma)005:285: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:286: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK016(ma)005:287: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK016(ma)005:288: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK016(ma)005:289: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK016(ma)005:290: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK016(ma)005:291: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK016(ma)005:292: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK016(ma)005:293: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK016(ma)005:294: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK016(ma)005:295: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK016(ma)005:296: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)005:297: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:298: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK016(ma)005:299: rdo rje rgyal po khyed la brten nas ni //
NK016(ma)005:300: sangs rgyas zhing sbyang 'gro la sman slad du //
NK016(ma)005:301: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:302: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgya mngon sprul te //
NK016(ma)005:303: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK016(ma)005:304: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK016(ma)005:305: khyed kyi zhabs gyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK016(ma)005:306: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed gyis mkhyen //
NK016(ma)005:307: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK016(ma)005:308: sems can don la myur du bdag mchi na //
NK016(ma)005:309: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:310: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:311: ye shes kyi 'khor lo thams cad mkha' khyab tu sad par byas te /
NK016(ma)005:312: h'u a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hohs ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:313: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK016(ma)005:314: khyad par bstan pa'i dus mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i byin
NK016(ma)005:315: gyis rlob pa'i dbang mchog bskur ba'i dngos grub stsol
NK016(ma)005:316: ba'i mthu chen bdud 'dul bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)005:317: byin chen byin phob bcom dbang chen dbang bskur dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)005:318: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:319: spos bsreg cing rol mo sna tshogs kyi sgra sbyar te /
NK016(ma)005:320: h'u h'u h'u h'u zhes byin bsdus pas /
NK016(ma)005:321: mkha' khyab kyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag gnas yo
NK016(ma)005:322: byad rnams la thim ste sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK016(ma)005:323: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor byin gyis brlabs par bsam
NK016(ma)005:324: mo // drug pa mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:325: mchod rdzas rnams ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ais bsang /
NK016(ma)005:326: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aas sbyang /
NK016(ma)005:327: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las a /
NK016(ma)005:333: nam mkha'i khams thams cad khyab /
NK016(ma)005:335: 'khor 'das kyi rtsi bcud thams cad bsdus nas mchod rdzas rnams la thim par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:336: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:337: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+aa pe d+h+au /
NK016(ma)005:340: bde mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po'i rol pa las /
NK016(ma)005:341: rdo rje zhabs bsil ma la sogs pa mchod pa'i
NK016(ma)005:342: lha mo khrus gzhong dang spos khang man+d+ha ra'i me
NK016(ma)005:343: tog la sogs pa thogs pa nam mkha' gang ba
NK016(ma)005:344: rnams su gyur par bsam pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK016(ma)005:347: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad /
NK016(ma)005:348: b+h+au bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala b+h+r+au /
NK016(ma)005:349: bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus
NK016(ma)005:350: su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar mi sha
NK016(ma)005:352: shar du ba lang gi sha dang dri chen /
NK016(ma)005:353: lhor khyi sha dang sha chen /
NK016(ma)005:354: nub tu rta sha dang rak+ta /
NK016(ma)005:355: byang du glang po che'i sha dang dri chu rnams kyi steng du rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:360: h+aa t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:361: s+pha sam 'od zer 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)005:367: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams su gyur /
NK016(ma)005:370: dbus su mi bskyod pa yab yum mthing ga /
NK016(ma)005:373: shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK016(ma)005:376: lhor rin 'byung yab yum ser po /
NK016(ma)005:379: nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK016(ma)005:382: byang du don grub yab yum ljang gu rnams su gyur /
NK016(ma)005:384: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)005:385: a nu r+aa ga ya myi /
NK016(ma)005:386: dzah h'u bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+tah s+pha ra sam
NK016(ma)005:387: ha rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas
NK016(ma)005:388: zhu ba las byung ba'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK016(ma)005:389: gyis mtshan pa'i kha gcod rdo rje rgya gram gyi
NK016(ma)005:390: lte bar / pad+man+ta kri ta badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:391: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma dang rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pa lte ba yan chad thon pa /
NK016(ma)005:393: shar du mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:394: lhor khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa nub tu
NK016(ma)005:395: ro langs ma dmar mo lcags sgrog byang du ral
NK016(ma)005:396: gcig ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa gyi 'od
NK016(ma)005:397: zer gyis 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams cad bkug
NK016(ma)005:398: / dam tshig gi bdud rtsi dang gnyis su med
NK016(ma)005:399: par gyur pa las ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya
NK016(ma)005:400: mtsho chen por gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:401: g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyi rdo rjes bdud rtsi la reg ste /
NK016(ma)005:402: +aahh+au sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aa /
NK016(ma)005:403: zhes rgya rtsa tsam bzlas shing /
NK016(ma)005:404: mthar g.yon bskor du dkrugs te /
NK016(ma)005:405: h'u h'u h'u h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK016(ma)005:406: yum bzhi bdud rtsi la thim par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:408: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+au pad+ma ba lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+au /
NK016(ma)005:409: gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK016(ma)005:410: du gtor rdzas 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang
NK016(ma)005:411: ba med pa la gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:412: s+pha sam ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim te
NK016(ma)005:413: ba la b+aa d+y+aa gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK016(ma)005:415: gzugs rdo rje ma sogs lha mo nam mkha' gang
NK016(ma)005:416: bas 'dod yon dpag tu med par spro ba'i bdag
NK016(ma)005:419: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+au b+hany+dza ka p+aa la b+h+r+au /
NK016(ma)005:420: dmar gyi dung chen yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK016(ma)005:421: du rak+ta la ra yig dmar pos mtshan par gyur
NK016(ma)005:422: / s+pha sam ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+auihth+aa /
NK016(ma)005:423: chags med rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pas nam mkha' gang bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:425: khyad par gyi sbyor ba sems bskyed pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:426: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos gnyis /
NK016(ma)005:431: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)005:432: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)005:433: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)005:434: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)005:436: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)005:437: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)005:438: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK016(ma)005:439: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK016(ma)005:440: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gag pa med las thams cad 'gag /
NK016(ma)005:442: e ma'o rdzogs pa'i gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK016(ma)005:443: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK016(ma)005:444: e ma'o rdzogs pa'i dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK016(ma)005:445: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK016(ma)005:446: e ma'o rdzogs pa'i 'gro 'ong med las 'gro dang 'ong //
NK016(ma)005:448: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos la /
NK016(ma)005:449: ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK016(ma)005:450: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK016(ma)005:451: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin spro ba /
NK016(ma)005:453: bskang ba bya ba dang lnga /
NK016(ma)005:456: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK016(ma)005:457: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK016(ma)005:458: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK016(ma)005:459: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:460: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs shing
NK016(ma)005:461: spros pa dang bral ba stong pa nyid du bsgom
NK016(ma)005:463: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK016(ma)005:464: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)005:465: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK016(ma)005:466: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK016(ma)005:467: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)005:468: sems can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK016(ma)005:469: snying rje chen po mkha' khyab tu bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:471: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK016(ma)005:473: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK016(ma)005:474: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK016(ma)005:475: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK016(ma)005:476: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK016(ma)005:477: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK016(ma)005:479: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:481: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:482: brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)005:484: dang po gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:485: sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med par gsal ba las /
NK016(ma)005:486: e yam wam lam sum ram rnams chad /
NK016(ma)005:487: s+pha sam 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)005:488: e las nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas 'byams klas pa'i dbyings su /
NK016(ma)005:489: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu g.yo ba'i ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK016(ma)005:490: wam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po /
NK016(ma)005:491: lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi /
NK016(ma)005:492: sum las rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin gyi ri rab zur bzhi pa /
NK016(ma)005:493: ram las me'i khor yug nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'bar ba'o //
NK016(ma)005:494: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:495: ri rab kyi steng du rgyu'i a las b+h+r+au chad /
NK016(ma)005:496: s+pha sam b+h+r+au bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+au /
NK016(ma)005:497: b+h+r+au yig yongs su gyur pa las ye shes rin
NK016(ma)005:498: po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang phyi nang gnyis
NK016(ma)005:499: rim gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK016(ma)005:500: nang nas rim pa bzhin mthing dkar ser dmar ljang
NK016(ma)005:501: ba'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan pa'i steng
NK016(ma)005:502: na rin po che'i pha gu ser po rin po
NK016(ma)005:503: che sna tshogs pas bkra ba 'phyar thabs su bkod
NK016(ma)005:504: pa'i mthar mu tig gi mgul 'khor 'phyang ba /
NK016(ma)005:505: de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la gser
NK016(ma)005:506: gyi ska rags bzhi'i phyi ngos su ma ka ra'i
NK016(ma)005:507: kha nas rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba
NK016(ma)005:508: phyed pa / dar dang rnga yab /
NK016(ma)005:510: zla ba rlung gis bskyod pa la sogs pas mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)005:511: de'i phyi ngos su bya 'dab las 'phyang ba'i rin po che'i shar bu /
NK016(ma)005:512: steng ngos su mda' yab pad+ma 'dab ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK016(ma)005:513: de dag gi bar bar du bum pa la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang /
NK016(ma)005:515: zur bzhir rnam par bkra ba'i gdugs kyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)005:516: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon
NK016(ma)005:517: gyi snam bu dmar pos bskor ba la gzugs rdo
NK016(ma)005:518: rje ma sogs lha mo rnams kyis mchod pa'i sprin
NK016(ma)005:520: sgo dang sgo khyud kyi mtshams dang zur bzhir zla
NK016(ma)005:521: ba phyed pa la gnas pa'i rdo rje nor bus
NK016(ma)005:522: brgyan pa / phyi ma'i sgo khang them skas dang
NK016(ma)005:523: bcas pa'i sgo logs kyi zur bzhi nas bum pa
NK016(ma)005:524: la gnas pa'i ka ba bzhi bzhis btegs pa'i rta
NK016(ma)005:525: babs snam bu brgyad pa bsil khang dang ldan pa'i
NK016(ma)005:526: rtse mor pad+ma la gnas pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK016(ma)005:527: gdugs kyis phub pa g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho
NK016(ma)005:529: gzhan yang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan sna tshogs
NK016(ma)005:530: pa dang gser gyi dril bu la sogs pas brgyan
NK016(ma)005:531: pa / sgo'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la t+aa la'i ljon pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:532: dpag bsam gyi shing la bkra shis pa'i bya snyan par sgrog pa sna tshogs gnas pa /
NK016(ma)005:533: shing de dag kyang gser gyi tha gus bres shing
NK016(ma)005:534: dril bu dang g.yer kha chos kyi sgra snyan par
NK016(ma)005:536: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i khrus kyi rdzing bu la lha mo sna tshogs bde bar rtse ba /
NK016(ma)005:537: rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba re re ste brgyad dang /
NK016(ma)005:538: gzhan yang rin po che sna bdun dang bkra shis
NK016(ma)005:539: pa'i rdzas brgyad sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad
NK016(ma)005:541: gzhal yas khang gi nang bar khyams gru bzhi pa
NK016(ma)005:542: nyis rim gyi nang ma gru chad dang bcas pa'i
NK016(ma)005:543: lte ba re'u mig dgu pa 'khor lo sum rim
NK016(ma)005:544: mu khyud dang bcas pas bskor ba'i phyogs bzhi nas
NK016(ma)005:545: rigs kyi mtshan ma can gyi ka ba brgyad kyis
NK016(ma)005:546: btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung zlum dang /
NK016(ma)005:547: gdung chen bzhis mig mang ris su bres pas mdzes
NK016(ma)005:548: par phub pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa'i rtse mo
NK016(ma)005:549: rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)005:550: phyi nang gnyis ka'i steng 'og thams cad shar dkar /
NK016(ma)005:554: dbus sngo ba dwangs shing sgrib pa med par kun
NK016(ma)005:555: tu gsal ba sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la
NK016(ma)005:556: rdzogs pa / de'i phyi rol du r+au dra longs
NK016(ma)005:557: spyod dang bcas par dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod
NK016(ma)005:558: chen po brgyad dur khrod kyi chos rnams kyis 'jigs
NK016(ma)005:559: par byas pa'i phyir nas rdo rje srung ba'i gur
NK016(ma)005:560: khang 'bar ba me'i 'od zer kun tu 'phro bas
NK016(ma)005:562: gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:563: gzhal yas khang gi lha gnas so sor gdan gyi
NK016(ma)005:564: rim pa gtso bo dang de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK016(ma)005:565: lnga'i gnas su seng+he glang po rta mchog rma bya
NK016(ma)005:566: shang shang rnams kyis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK016(ma)005:567: drug gi steng du pad nyi zla ba ste lnga
NK016(ma)005:568: brtsegs / che mchog dang khrag 'thung dgu'i gnas su
NK016(ma)005:569: pad zla nyi ma'i steng dregs pa can khyo shugs
NK016(ma)005:570: brtsegs / zung re / sems dpa' brgyad kyi gnas su pad nyi zla ba /
NK016(ma)005:573: sgo skyong bzhi rnams kyi gnas su nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan re re /
NK016(ma)005:574: thub pa drug gi gnas su pad rkyang dang /
NK016(ma)005:575: dbang mo rnams kyi gnas su zhing skam po'i gdan re re gsal bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:576: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK016(ma)005:581: rang gi sems nyid a dkar po dri ma med
NK016(ma)005:582: par gsal ba las zhi khro rigs brgya'i yi ge
NK016(ma)005:583: 'khor lo'i sprin phung rim pa bzhin spro ba ni
NK016(ma)005:589: che mchog dang khrag 'thung dgu'i gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:600: sems dpa' brgyad kyi gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:601: k+sh+aim tram h+r+aim dz+rim me th+l+him h'u m+au /
NK016(ma)005:602: h+au tram h+r+aim am dzahmh'u bam hoh gnas ma brgyad kyi gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:603: ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha /
NK016(ma)005:604: yul ma brgyad kyi gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:605: he he he he he he he he /
NK016(ma)005:606: thug pa drug gi gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:607: k+sh+aim t+r+aum srum pram k+sham ye /
NK016(ma)005:610: dzahh+au bam hoh sgo skyong bzhi'i gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:612: dbang mo rnams kyi gnas su /
NK016(ma)005:613: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:614: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:615: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:616: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:618: nyi shu rtsa brgyad po khyams phyi ma'i phyogs rer drug drug dang /
NK016(ma)005:620: thams cad kyang lha rang rang gi kha dog tu gsal bar gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)005:621: a zhes brjod pas gzhi'i a de 'od du zhu
NK016(ma)005:622: nas yig 'bru rnams la khyab par thim pas shin
NK016(ma)005:626: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK016(ma)005:628: slar 'dus nas yig 'bru rnams la thim pa 'od
NK016(ma)005:629: du zhu ba las zhi khro rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:632: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bcom ldan 'das
NK016(ma)005:633: dpal kun tu bzang po sku mdog mthing ga in+d+ra
NK016(ma)005:634: n+ai la'i lhun po la nyi ma shar ba ltar
NK016(ma)005:637: zhi zhing rab tu 'dzum pa'i mdangs gsal ba'i zhal
NK016(ma)005:638: gyi 'gyur ba ting nge 'dzin gyis rnam par rol
NK016(ma)005:639: pa'i nyams can mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba
NK016(ma)005:640: / phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)005:641: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis brtan par bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:642: a a a badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta ah de'i
NK016(ma)005:643: phang du yum kun tu bzang mo mthing ga zhal
NK016(ma)005:645: phyag gnyis kyis yab la 'khyud cing pad+ma'i skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)005:646: gnyis ka'ang lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK016(ma)005:648: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan /
NK016(ma)005:650: gar gyi phu rung ste dar gyi chas gos lnga dang /
NK016(ma)005:657: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK016(ma)005:658: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can gsal 'tsher lhun
NK016(ma)005:659: sdug gzi byin ldan pa ste zhi ba'i nyams dgu
NK016(ma)005:660: rgyas pa / sangs rgyas kyi sprin phung mtha' yas
NK016(ma)005:661: par 'char ba'i 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang
NK016(ma)005:662: ba re re yang bye ba phrag drug drug tu
NK016(ma)005:663: 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i klong na bde stong gnyis su
NK016(ma)005:664: med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:665: lha rnams kyi gsang sngags brjod pa tsam gyis so
NK016(ma)005:666: so'i sa bon rnams lha de dang de'i skur bkra
NK016(ma)005:667: lam gyis gsal bar gyur pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:670: gtso bo'i g.yas su mi bskyod pa sngon po g.yas
NK016(ma)005:671: rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur
NK016(ma)005:673: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo g.yas
NK016(ma)005:674: dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon rdo
NK016(ma)005:676: de'i phyi rol gyi re'u mig bzhi la /
NK016(ma)005:679: shar du rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo g.yon
NK016(ma)005:680: dril bu spyan ma dkar mo g.yas dril bu g.yon
NK016(ma)005:683: lhor rin 'byung ser po g.yas rin po che g.yon
NK016(ma)005:684: dril bu m+aa ma k+ai ser mo g.yas dril bu
NK016(ma)005:685: g.yon rin po che +aam +aa ro lika /
NK016(ma)005:687: nub tu snang mtha' dmar po g.yas pad+ma g.yon dril
NK016(ma)005:688: bu gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas dril bu g.yon
NK016(ma)005:691: byang du don grub ljang gu g.yas rgya gram g.yon
NK016(ma)005:692: dril bu dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu g.yas dril
NK016(ma)005:693: bu g.yon rgya gram thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:694: yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK016(ma)005:695: yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:696: thams cad kyang rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:697: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:698: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gtso bo'i mdun du dpal
NK016(ma)005:699: chen po che mchog he ru ka sku mdog mthing
NK016(ma)005:700: nag 'bar ba chen po'i 'od zer can /
NK016(ma)005:702: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK016(ma)005:703: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum pa /
NK016(ma)005:704: sma ra dang smin ma dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu skra gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK016(ma)005:707: g.yon dmar gyis gang ba'i dung chen steng 'og tu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)005:708: sgeg pa la sogs pa'i gar dgu'i nyams kyis rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:709: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK016(ma)005:710: glang po che'i ko bas stod g.yogs shing /
NK016(ma)005:711: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs grol pa /
NK016(ma)005:712: thod pa skam po lnga rigs lnga'i rtse phran can gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK016(ma)005:713: rlon pa lnga bcu'i do shal 'phyang ba /
NK016(ma)005:714: rus pa'i rgyan drug dang sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)005:715: khrag zhag thal ba sogs dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas can /
NK016(ma)005:716: zhabs g.yon bskum zhing g.yas brkyang pa'i dor stabs kyis
NK016(ma)005:717: dbang phyug khyo shug gi mgo bo dang nu ma
NK016(ma)005:718: nas bardzisa pa / yum gnam zhal dbyings kyi dbang
NK016(ma)005:719: phyug ma sngon mo gcer bu skra grol zhing lang
NK016(ma)005:720: nas bardzisa pa / tshos sgeg pa / g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK016(ma)005:721: g.yon dung dmar stob pa'i tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:722: gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs sogs dur khrod rol
NK016(ma)005:723: pa'i chas can zhabs g.yon brkyang zhing g.yas bskum pas
NK016(ma)005:724: gtso bo dang dgyes par 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)005:725: stong pa nyid dang snying rje dbyer med pa'i bdag
NK016(ma)005:726: nyid can ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong
NK016(ma)005:727: na bzhugs pa'o // badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK016(ma)005:728: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:729: gtso bo'i g.yon du rdo rje khrag 'thung mthing nag g.yas rdo rje dang /
NK016(ma)005:731: khrag 'thung dgu'i phyag g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa'ang yod do //
NK016(ma)005:732: rdo rje khrag 'thung ma dang mnyam par sbyor zhing dregs pa pho mo'i gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:733: 'khor lo nang ma rtsibs brgyad pa la rim bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:734: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK016(ma)005:735: bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:736: shar du sangs rgyas khrag 'thung smug nag g.yas 'khor lo dang g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:737: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung ma dang mnyam par sbyor zhing
NK016(ma)005:738: lha chen pho mo'i rat+na sh+w+ai he ru ka h'u
NK016(ma)005:740: lhor rin chen khrag 'thung ser nag g.yas rin po
NK016(ma)005:741: che dang g.yon dung rin chen khrag 'thung ma dang
NK016(ma)005:742: mnyam par sbyor zhing gshin rje pho mo'i pad+ma sh+w+ai
NK016(ma)005:744: pad+ma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:745: nub tu pad+ma khrag 'thung dmar nag g.yas pad+ma dang
NK016(ma)005:746: g.yon dung pad+ma khrag 'thung ma dang mnyam par sbyor
NK016(ma)005:747: zhing klu dbang pho mo'i karma sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK016(ma)005:748: h'u / karma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:749: byang du las kyi khrag 'thung ljang nag g.yas rgya
NK016(ma)005:750: gram dang g.yon dung las kyi khrag 'thung ma dang
NK016(ma)005:751: mnyam par sbyor zhing gnod sbyin pho mo'i rak+sha sh+r+ai
NK016(ma)005:753: rak+sha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:754: shar lhor rak+sha he ru ka mthing nag g.yas dbyug
NK016(ma)005:755: to dang g.yon dung rak+sha dbyings phyug ma dang mnyam
NK016(ma)005:756: par sbyor zhing me lha pho mo'i sa nu sh+r+ai
NK016(ma)005:758: sa nu kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:759: lho nub tu sa nu he ru ka ser nag
NK016(ma)005:760: g.yas dgra s+t+wa dang g.yon dung sa nu dbyings phyug
NK016(ma)005:761: ma dang mnyam par sbyor zhing srin po pho mo'i
NK016(ma)005:762: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK016(ma)005:763: gu h+ya kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:764: nub byang du gu h+ya he ru ka dud kha
NK016(ma)005:765: g.yas ral gri dang g.yon dung gu h+ya dbyings phyug
NK016(ma)005:766: ma dang mnyam par sbyor zhing rlung lha pho mo'i
NK016(ma)005:767: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u /
NK016(ma)005:768: yak+sha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h'u /
NK016(ma)005:769: byang shar du yak+sha he ru ljang nag g.yas be con dang g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:770: yak+sha dbyings phyug ma dang mnyam par sbyor zhing dbang ldan pho mo'i gdan la rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:771: yum rnams yab kyi mdog can g.yas dril bu dang
NK016(ma)005:772: g.yon dung dmar stob pa'i tshul can te thams cad
NK016(ma)005:773: kyang gar dgu'i ros sgeg cing dur khrod rol pa'i
NK016(ma)005:775: 'khor lo bar ma rtsibs brgyad pa la rim bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:777: h'u l+aa s+ye ma ya ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:778: shar du sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:779: sgeg mo dkar mo khu tshur gyi rgyas me long bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)005:781: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh lhor nam snying
NK016(ma)005:782: ser po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon phreng ba ma
NK016(ma)005:783: ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba h+r+aim h+aa h'u
NK016(ma)005:786: nub tu spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad+ma dang g.yon glu ma dmar mo pi wam /
NK016(ma)005:788: am n+ai rte r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)005:789: byang du phyag rdor mthing ga g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa /
NK016(ma)005:790: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:792: shar lhor byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing dang
NK016(ma)005:793: g.yon spos ma dkar ser spos khang th+l+him ni s+sa
NK016(ma)005:796: lho nub tu sgrib sel dmar ser g.yas glegs bam
NK016(ma)005:797: dang g.yon me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi
NK016(ma)005:798: phreng ba h'u sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:799: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK016(ma)005:800: nub byang du kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po
NK016(ma)005:801: che'i snye ma dang g.yon mar me ma dmar ljang
NK016(ma)005:802: mar me m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa
NK016(ma)005:804: byang shar du 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas ut+pala dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:805: dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung phor bsnams pa ste /
NK016(ma)005:806: yab rnams g.yas brkyang ba'i phyed skyil la yum rnams g.yon brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis 'khyud pa //
NK016(ma)005:807: thams cad kyang dar gyi na bza' dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:808: 'khor lo phyi ma rtsibs bcu drug pa'i phyogs mtshams brgyad por /
NK016(ma)005:810: shar du goo ri ma sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug dang g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:812: lhor tsoo r+ai ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'geng sa ba /
NK016(ma)005:813: badz+ra pra mo he h+ai ha /
NK016(ma)005:814: nub tu pra mo dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK016(ma)005:816: byang du be ta l+ai nag mo rdo rje dang zhing chung 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:818: shar lhor puk+ka s+ai dmar ser zhing chung gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK016(ma)005:820: lho nub tu g+hasma r+ai ljang gu g.yon gyi dung khrag g.yas pa'i rdo rjes dkrug pa /
NK016(ma)005:822: nub byang du sma sha mthing nag byis pa'i ro bzung nas snying za ba /
NK016(ma)005:824: byang shar du tsan+da l+ai ser skya zhing chung gi mgo lus 'dral ba /
NK016(ma)005:825: thams cad kyang gcer bu lang tshos sgeg cing khro 'dzum bzhad pa /
NK016(ma)005:826: dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK016(ma)005:827: g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:828: phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhi'i g.yon logs kyi rtsibs rnams su rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:830: seng gdong ma ser mo ro za zhing lag gnyis thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK016(ma)005:831: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:832: stag gdong ma dmar mo lag gnyis mthur du bsnol bas ro bzung ba /
NK016(ma)005:833: badz+ra sh+r+ai g+aa la mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:834: wa gdong ma nag mo zhing chung lces ldag pa /
NK016(ma)005:835: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:836: spyang gdong ma mthing nag zhing chung gi khog pa 'dral ba ste mche ba can bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)005:837: mtshams kyi rtsibs bzhi'i g.yon logs kyi rtsibs rnams su rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:838: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:839: rgod gdong ma dmar mo zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK016(ma)005:841: kang+ka'i gdong ma dmar skya bam ro phrag par khur ba /
NK016(ma)005:842: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:843: bya rog gdong can nag mo ral gri dang b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:844: badz+ra u l+au k+aa mu kh+ai he /
NK016(ma)005:845: 'ug gdong ma mthing nag rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa ste gshog pa can bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)005:846: thams cad kyang gcer bu rang rang khros pa'i zhal can dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:848: khyams nang ma'i shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:849: mu ne h'u t+r+aum s+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:850: byang du lha min gyi thub pa mthing ga go cha mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:851: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par mu ne pram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:852: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa dmar nag pusti mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:853: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag
NK016(ma)005:854: rin po che'i sgrom bu mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK016(ma)005:855: / byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:856: thams cad kyang mchog gi sprul sku'i cha byad can 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:857: khyams nang ma'i sgo phubs bzhi la /
NK016(ma)005:859: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:860: shar sgor gshin rje gshed smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs pa 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:861: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa dang rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:863: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro lho sgor stobs po che
NK016(ma)005:864: ser nag rdo rje zhags pa ma ser nag zhags
NK016(ma)005:866: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro nub sgor rta mgrin dmar
NK016(ma)005:867: nag thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa lcags sgrog ma
NK016(ma)005:868: dmar nag lcags sgrog h'u big+h+n+aan+ta kri phata /
NK016(ma)005:869: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil
NK016(ma)005:870: pa ljang nag rgya gram dril bu ma ljang nag
NK016(ma)005:871: dril bu 'dzin pa dang rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:872: thams cad kyang khro gtum mi bzad pa'i nyams can gyad kyi 'dor stabs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:873: mthar byed bzhi'i phyi ngos kyi sgo g.yabs bzhi la /
NK016(ma)005:874: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah shar sgor rta gdong ma sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:876: lhor sgor phag gdong ma nag mo zhags pa badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK016(ma)005:877: nub sgor seng gdong ma dmar mo lcags sgrog badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh /
NK016(ma)005:878: byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:886: shar stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:887: srin mo dmar ser g.yag gdong tri shul 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:888: tshangs ma dmar skya sbrul gdong rdo rje rtse lnga
NK016(ma)005:889: 'khrug mo ser nag gzig gdong dbyug to dang sdigs
NK016(ma)005:890: mdzub / brgya byin ma dkar dmar sre mong mgo
NK016(ma)005:891: can thod khrag khyab 'jug seer mo pha wang mgo
NK016(ma)005:892: can 'khor lo dbang mo dmar skya dred gdong bam
NK016(ma)005:893: mdzub / dbyug 'dzin pa'o // badz+ra ping+ga lam b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:899: lho stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:900: zhi ba dmar mo dom mgo can rgyu zhags bdud
NK016(ma)005:901: rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin mgo can bum pa
NK016(ma)005:902: zhi ba ma sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo can pun+da
NK016(ma)005:903: ri ka be con ma nag mo khra mgo can
NK016(ma)005:904: thod rlon srin mo dmar nag wa gdong rgyu zhags
NK016(ma)005:905: za byed nag mo stag mgo bam chen 'dzin pa'o
NK016(ma)005:908: e ka tsa ri n+ai b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:912: nub stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:913: dga' byed dmar mo rgod gdong khog chen khrag 'thung
NK016(ma)005:914: ma dmar nag rta gdong rdo rje'i dbyug pa gcig
NK016(ma)005:915: spyod ma dkar dmar khyung gdong b+han dmar 'dod pa
NK016(ma)005:916: dmar ser khyi gdong byis bam nor srung dkar dmar
NK016(ma)005:917: pra shud mgo can pad+ma rlung mo dmar skya sha
NK016(ma)005:918: ba'i mgo can ba dan 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:919: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:925: byang stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK016(ma)005:926: gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdog rnge'u chung ma
NK016(ma)005:927: mo dmar ser skyin gdong me sgron phag mo ljang
NK016(ma)005:928: ser phag gdong mche ba rgan byed ljang sngon khwa
NK016(ma)005:929: ta'i mgo can dung khrag sna chen ljang dmar ba
NK016(ma)005:930: lang mgo can bam chen chu lha ma ljang nag
NK016(ma)005:931: sbrul gdong bdud rtsi'i thod pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:932: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:936: shar sgor nag mo chen po khu byug mgo can
NK016(ma)005:937: lcags kyu lho sgor rdo rje ra mo sngon mo
NK016(ma)005:938: ra gdong rgyu zhags nub sgor bum sna ma dmar
NK016(ma)005:939: mo seng gdong / lcags sgrog byang sgor gsus 'dzin
NK016(ma)005:940: ma ljang nag skya ga'i mgo can dril bu 'dzin
NK016(ma)005:941: mo seng gdong / pa / thams cad kyang drag
NK016(ma)005:942: mo'i gzugs can dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas kyis brgyan
NK016(ma)005:943: te zhing gi gdan la rol pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:944: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi'i khor yug la khro bo chen po yab yum bcu /
NK016(ma)005:948: sprul pa'i ging chen pho mo /
NK016(ma)005:951: 'bar ma brgyad la sogs te sprul pa dang yang
NK016(ma)005:952: sprul bka' sdod dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs mtha' yas
NK016(ma)005:953: pa dang bcas pa rnams kyang rang rang gi rgyan
NK016(ma)005:954: dang cha lugs dang ldan cing so so'i 'khor gyis
NK016(ma)005:955: bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo nyi ma dang
NK016(ma)005:956: 'od zer gyi tshul du mngon par snang ba'i sgyu
NK016(ma)005:957: 'phrul gyi rol mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa dam
NK016(ma)005:958: tshig gi 'khor lor rdzogs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:959: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:960: de ltar gsal ba'i lha tshogs thams cad kyi srog
NK016(ma)005:961: gi gor rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan
NK016(ma)005:962: dang phyag mtshan spangs pa re re'i thugs kar so
NK016(ma)005:963: so'i phyag mtshan gyi lte bar sa bon la sngags
NK016(ma)005:964: phreng gis bskor bas mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:965: sa bon rnams las 'od zer 'phros pas phyogs bcu
NK016(ma)005:966: dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dbang gi
NK016(ma)005:967: lha rigs lnga yab yum gyi rnam par badz+ra sa
NK016(ma)005:968: m+aa dzahs spyan drangs par bsam /
NK016(ma)005:969: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:971: de rnams gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK016(ma)005:972: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)005:973: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bas
NK016(ma)005:974: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:975: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur /
NK016(ma)005:976: chu'i lhag ma sbyir bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK016(ma)005:977: pa las rang rigs bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga
NK016(ma)005:978: sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan par mos
NK016(ma)005:979: la / phung po lnga dag pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su nga rgyal bya /
NK016(ma)005:980: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya gnas so sor 'jog cing dbang sngags brjod pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:981: de yang rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa rigs bdag tu byas pa la mtshon na /
NK016(ma)005:982: rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)005:983: ma h+aa sh+aunya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:984: phyag rgya de las 'dzub mo gnyis brkyang ba dpral bar bzhag la /
NK016(ma)005:985: ma h+aa +aa dar dz+ny+aa na srin lag brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas par /
NK016(ma)005:986: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na mthe bong brkyang pa ltag par /
NK016(ma)005:987: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na mathe'u chung brkyang pa rna ltag g.yon par /
NK016(ma)005:988: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na zhes pas gtso bo zhi khro /
NK016(ma)005:990: rdo rje khrag 'thung rnams yum dang bcas pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:991: thub pa drug la mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur
NK016(ma)005:992: pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan gyis dbu brgyan par gyur
NK016(ma)005:993: / des mtshon nas rigs gzhan bzhi la'ang rigs gang
NK016(ma)005:994: yin de'i sngags dang por brjod cing phyag rgya spyi
NK016(ma)005:996: gang dbus su song ba'i sngags rgya dang rigs bdag gi shul du mi bskyod pa 'jog pa ste /
NK016(ma)005:997: rnam snang gi dbang rgya dang +aa dar+sha dang por brjod pa'i sngags mtshan lngas /
NK016(ma)005:1000: rak+sha he ru ka sa snying /
NK016(ma)005:1002: gshin rje gshed rnams yum dang bcas pa la rnam
NK016(ma)005:1003: snang bdag por sa ma t+aa dang por brjod pa'i
NK016(ma)005:1009: stobs po che rnams yum dang bcas pa la rin
NK016(ma)005:1010: 'byung bdag por pra t+ya dang por brjod pa'i sngags
NK016(ma)005:1016: rta mgrin rnams yum dang bcas pa la snang mtha'
NK016(ma)005:1017: bdag por kri t+y+aa dang pod brjod sngags tshan lngas
NK016(ma)005:1023: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams yum dang bcas pa la
NK016(ma)005:1024: don grub bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i cod pan
NK016(ma)005:1026: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag ste sh+au nya t+aa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK016(ma)005:1027: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu dang /
NK016(ma)005:1028: dbang mo nyer brgyad la dbang bskur bas spyi bor
NK016(ma)005:1029: rdo rje rtse lnga pa re res dbu brgyan par
NK016(ma)005:1030: bsam mo // gsum pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1031: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK016(ma)005:1032: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)005:1033: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)005:1035: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:1036: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor
NK016(ma)005:1037: lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam la nga rgyal
NK016(ma)005:1038: bya zhing rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs te
NK016(ma)005:1039: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:1040: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po /
NK016(ma)005:1041: de'i 'od zer gyis gsung rdo rje'i +aam la thim /
NK016(ma)005:1042: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung +aam yongs
NK016(ma)005:1043: su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma rdo
NK016(ma)005:1044: rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK016(ma)005:1046: snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h'u sngon po /
NK016(ma)005:1047: de'i 'od zer gyis thugs rdo rje'i h'u la thim /
NK016(ma)005:1048: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs h'u yongs
NK016(ma)005:1049: su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo
NK016(ma)005:1050: rje rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar sarba ta th+aa
NK016(ma)005:1051: ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta zhes brjod cing sku gsung
NK016(ma)005:1052: thugs rdo rje gsum du nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:1053: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la drug /
NK016(ma)005:1054: ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang ba /
NK016(ma)005:1063: rig pa'i me tog dor ba /
NK016(ma)005:1064: dngos grub bskul te bstim pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:1066: rang gi thugs kar dwangs ma'i srog h'u mthing ga
NK016(ma)005:1067: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rtag tu 'char bzhin pa
NK016(ma)005:1068: / de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu
NK016(ma)005:1069: dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bskul pas
NK016(ma)005:1070: / / chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las
NK016(ma)005:1071: gzugs sku zhi khro rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:1072: chen por sad par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1073: lag gnyis lcags kyu'i rgya dang bcas pas /
NK016(ma)005:1075: stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK016(ma)005:1076: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK016(ma)005:1077: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1078: rdo rje sems dpa' khyod bdag skal bzang dpal //
NK016(ma)005:1079: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:1080: zhes pas snyan gsan phab la /
NK016(ma)005:1083: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK016(ma)005:1084: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK016(ma)005:1085: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK016(ma)005:1086: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK016(ma)005:1087: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)005:1088: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yis //
NK016(ma)005:1089: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:1090: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK016(ma)005:1091: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahmh'uhbam ho ru lu ru lu h'u /
NK016(ma)005:1092: zhes pas dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang nye bar spyan drangs te //
NK016(ma)005:1093: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK016(ma)005:1094: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK016(ma)005:1095: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod la //
NK016(ma)005:1096: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK016(ma)005:1097: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas spros pa'i dzahmh'u bam hohs dgug bcings bsdams la dgyes pa bskyed nas /
NK016(ma)005:1098: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1102: h'u badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK016(ma)005:1103: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1106: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h'u /
NK016(ma)005:1107: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK016(ma)005:1108: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis kyi sku
NK016(ma)005:1109: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams gnyis su med
NK016(ma)005:1112: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)005:1113: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK016(ma)005:1114: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)005:1115: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK016(ma)005:1118: h'u badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes dang //
NK016(ma)005:1119: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)005:1120: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:1121: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che /
NK016(ma)005:1122: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK016(ma)005:1123: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+aam /
NK016(ma)005:1124: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK016(ma)005:1125: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh zhes dngos grub
NK016(ma)005:1126: skul bas ye shes kyi 'khor lo dang gnyis med
NK016(ma)005:1127: du dgyes pa bskyed pa las drin lan gyi tshul
NK016(ma)005:1129: a li u li t+aa li ta p+aa li damsh+ta
NK016(ma)005:1130: go n+aa roo tri kha ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa
NK016(ma)005:1132: dzahmh'u bam hoh h'u ha he phata /
NK016(ma)005:1134: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chu la chu bzhag pa
NK016(ma)005:1135: bzhin dbyer med du gyur nas gsal zhing brtan par
NK016(ma)005:1140: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs ka nas mar me
NK016(ma)005:1141: gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul du rang nyid gtso
NK016(ma)005:1142: bo gnyis pa'i rnam pas thon nas dkyil 'khor gyi
NK016(ma)005:1144: sems can thams cad dang bya byed thun mong par
NK016(ma)005:1145: gyur nas phyag dang mchod pa sogs las kyi rim
NK016(ma)005:1147: de'i dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1148: lus zhing rdul dang mnyam par sprul nas /
NK016(ma)005:1149: bla ma mnyam med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK016(ma)005:1150: dus gsum bde bshegs sras bcas thams cad kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1151: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin byin brlabs pa //
NK016(ma)005:1152: bka' drin chen po'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:1153: zhes rtsa ba'i bla ma la phyag byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:1155: kun bzang phyag rdor ku ku r+aa dza che //
NK016(ma)005:1156: in+d+ra b+hu ti sh+aakya pu tri'i zhabs //
NK016(ma)005:1157: sing+ha r+aa dza u pa r+aa dza la //
NK016(ma)005:1158: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)005:1159: go ma de bi rdo rje h+aum mdzad rtsal //
NK016(ma)005:1160: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la mi tra //
NK016(ma)005:1161: gnyags lo gzhon nu sog po lha dpal la //
NK016(ma)005:1162: sgo gsum gus pas gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sru legs sgron //
NK016(ma)005:1163: sras mchog gzhon snying zhu ston bsod nams mtshan //
NK016(ma)005:1164: bde gshegs zur chen zur chung shes rab grags //
NK016(ma)005:1165: sgo gsum gus pas glan dang 'gar ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan dpal //
NK016(ma)005:1166: rdor 'od bsod nams rgyal mtshan chos seng zhabs //
NK016(ma)005:1167: sangs rgyas dpal ba bsod nams mgon po la //
NK016(ma)005:1168: sgo gsum gus pas sgrol chen bsam rdor thugs sras sangs rin zhabs //
NK016(ma)005:1169: 'gos lo gzhon dpal bsod nams rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK016(ma)005:1170: se ston rin rgyan rgya hor rdo rje rtsal //
NK016(ma)005:1171: sgo gsum gus pas pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal bdud 'joms rje //
NK016(ma)005:1172: tshe ring dbang po ngag dbang phun tshogs mtshan //
NK016(ma)005:1173: brgyud srol kun 'dus rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK016(ma)005:1174: sgo gsum gus pas lo chen chos dpal rgyal sras rin rnam zhabs //
NK016(ma)005:1175: pad+ma bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK016(ma)005:1176: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i dpal /
NK016(ma)005:1177: sgo gsum gus pas bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer 'bar //
NK016(ma)005:1178: khyab bdag drin chen rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK016(ma)005:1179: rab 'byams zhi khro dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lhar //
NK016(ma)005:1180: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)005:1181: zhes brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs kyi tshigs rkang bzhi pa bsgyur ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:1182: gzhan yang brgyud tshul du ma yod pa las gang mos pa de dang der bsgyur bas chog go //
NK016(ma)005:1184: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)005:1185: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)005:1186: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)005:1187: zhi khro rab 'byams tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:1188: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:1189: bya ba byed dang yid chos rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)005:1190: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:1191: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK016(ma)005:1192: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du sor sor gsal //
NK016(ma)005:1193: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:1194: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la ngo 'tshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)005:1195: dus gsum sras bcas thams cad bskyed mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)005:1196: rig sa kyi yum gyur rnams la rnam shes dbang po dag pas thugs dang gsung //
NK016(ma)005:1197: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyis sras mchog ste //
NK016(ma)005:1198: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la sgeg mo phreng thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK016(ma)005:1199: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pas rgyal ba mchod //
NK016(ma)005:1200: byang chub lha mo'i tshogs la bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK016(ma)005:1201: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK016(ma)005:1202: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams la drag shul thubs kyis 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)005:1203: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo bzhi thub par srung //
NK016(ma)005:1204: mthar byed sgo ba bzhi la phyag rtag chad lta 'byin gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK016(ma)005:1205: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril 'khrol ma //
NK016(ma)005:1206: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag steng 'og phyogs bzhi 'jig rten 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK016(ma)005:1207: nyon mongs drug 'joms rgyud drug dag par sbyor //
NK016(ma)005:1208: bcom ldan thub pa drugs la phyag 'jig rten 'das pa'i dus su sngon byung ba //
NK016(ma)005:1209: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:1210: dpal chen khrag 'thung rnams la phyag khro mo dbang phyug sku la 'khril mdzad cing //
NK016(ma)005:1211: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK016(ma)005:1212: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum rnams la phyag 'tshal //
NK016(ma)005:1213: bskal ba me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK016(ma)005:1214: ye shes sku mchog 'jigs byed slas su bzhugs //
NK016(ma)005:1215: khro mo chen mo brgyad la phyag nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK016(ma)005:1216: 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK016(ma)005:1217: phra men chen mo brgyad la phyag rdo rje gdong mo pho nya mgyogs ma bzhi //
NK016(ma)005:1218: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi thub par bsrung //
NK016(ma)005:1219: sgo skyong khro mo bzhi la dpal gyi 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra l+ai //
NK016(ma)005:1220: mkha' la shugs 'gro ma tshogs dbang phyug ma //
NK016(ma)005:1221: rnal 'byor nyi shu brgyad la phyag phyogs bcu dregs pa bsnol ba'i gnad steng na //
NK016(ma)005:1222: ye shes bskal pa me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK016(ma)005:1223: bdud 'dul yab yum rnams la phyag dmigs med chod
NK016(ma)005:1224: kyi sku la phyag longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK016(ma)005:1225: phyag cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag mi 'gyur
NK016(ma)005:1226: rdo rje'i sku la phyag mngon par byang chub sku
NK016(ma)005:1227: la phyag dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis bsgrubs pa
NK016(ma)005:1228: yi // tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing yon tan mthar phyin pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:1229: sku dang ye shes tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:1230: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes pa tsam mam /
NK016(ma)005:1231: 'grub tu rung na phyag gi bkol byang rgyas pa bzhin ci nus su bya ba gal che'o //
NK016(ma)005:1232: gnyis pa mchod pa la bcu bzhi las /
NK016(ma)005:1235: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)005:1236: de rnams kyi steng du h'u s+w+aa +amo h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1237: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)005:1238: de dag gi steng du m+aum lam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1239: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las //
NK016(ma)005:1240: sbyar ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK016(ma)005:1241: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK016(ma)005:1242: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK016(ma)005:1243: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:1244: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK016(ma)005:1246: zhes pas phyag rgya mdun du bsgyur nas g.yon du dgrol /
NK016(ma)005:1247: de'i tshe lhar gsal ba phyag chen sa bon chos rgya /
NK016(ma)005:1250: de nas khro bo'i tshogs kyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK016(ma)005:1251: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i nga rgyal byas la
NK016(ma)005:1252: / khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK016(ma)005:1253: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)005:1254: sku yi gar stabs klog 'gyu ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:1255: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK016(ma)005:1257: spro na rngam glog dang he ru 'dus par gsungs pa'i phyag rgya rnams las /
NK016(ma)005:1258: dkyil 'khor 'di'i lha grangs dang mtshungs pa tsam sbyar na shin tu'ang skabs su babs par 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)005:1260: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK016(ma)005:1262: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK016(ma)005:1263: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1264: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK016(ma)005:1265: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol /
NK016(ma)005:1266: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa
NK016(ma)005:1267: mu khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi
NK016(ma)005:1268: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1270: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK016(ma)005:1271: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK016(ma)005:1272: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil nas kyang //
NK016(ma)005:1273: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1274: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+ya d+ha ra
NK016(ma)005:1275: p+au dzi te na mah sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga
NK016(ma)005:1276: ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1278: so so'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK016(ma)005:1280: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa ma //
NK016(ma)005:1282: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK016(ma)005:1283: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i mchod par rol //
NK016(ma)005:1284: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK016(ma)005:1286: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)005:1288: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK016(ma)005:1289: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au be d+h+au /
NK016(ma)005:1292: snying rje thabs dang badz+ra push+pe'i pa na sogs nas /
NK016(ma)005:1294: dbang gi phyag na sgron ma bsnams //
NK016(ma)005:1296: dga' ba badz+r+aa lo ke'i pa na sogs /
NK016(ma)005:1297: +aa lo ke h+r+aihtsan+dana bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK016(ma)005:1302: lha mo rnams kyis dkyil 'khor pa rnams mchod nas
NK016(ma)005:1303: shangs la sogs pa'i dbang po so so la thim
NK016(ma)005:1305: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:1306: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:1307: mchod chen thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:1309: lha mo rnams slar byung ste rang gi gnas bzhir
NK016(ma)005:1310: thim pas sku gsung thugs phrin las bzhi'i dngos grub
NK016(ma)005:1314: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK016(ma)005:1315: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK016(ma)005:1316: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK016(ma)005:1317: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK016(ma)005:1318: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK016(ma)005:1319: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK016(ma)005:1320: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi sman //
NK016(ma)005:1321: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rnal 'byor che //
NK016(ma)005:1322: bde gshegs zhi ba'i thugs dam nyid //

NK016(ma)005:1368: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
