NK016(ma)005:1371: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:1372: 'gro ba'i don mdzad sprul sku thub drug la //
NK016(ma)005:1373: sman mchod sarba tshogs rje tshogs bdag che mchog he ru ka /
NK016(ma)005:1374: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khro rgyal yab yum dang //
NK016(ma)005:1375: gnas yul phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK016(ma)005:1377: sarba ma ltar byams shing sring ltar rab gdung ma //
NK016(ma)005:1378: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:1379: ma tshogs dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK016(ma)005:1380: sman mchod sarba dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dam can srung ma'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:1381: zhing skyong gzhi bdag rigs drug pha ma sogs //
NK016(ma)005:1382: srid gsum ka dag rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK016(ma)005:1383: sman mchod sarba ta th+aa zhes gu h+ya lag gi
NK016(ma)005:1384: phyag rgyas gtor bas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i zegs
NK016(ma)005:1385: ma'i sprin las bdud rtsi'i char babs pas dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:1386: pa thams cad mnyes shing tshims par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1387: mthar dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1388: rang gi lce la h'u yig dang /
NK016(ma)005:1389: sman gyi steng du 'bru gsum bsgoms te /
NK016(ma)005:1391: rdo rje lce yi dam tshig la //
NK016(ma)005:1392: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum bsgom //
NK016(ma)005:1393: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK016(ma)005:1394: myang na dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)005:1395: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sing+ng+hi /
NK016(ma)005:1396: wa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sing+ng+hi h'u /
NK016(ma)005:1397: zhes rim par reg ste lce la bzhag pas sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1398: drug pa bdud rtsi gsang bsnan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1399: bdud rtsi'i rgyun b+hany+dzara lan gsum du sbreng zhing /
NK016(ma)005:1401: mi bskyod ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i rol la bsnams su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1402: a la la hoh byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog de nyid 'gog pa rnams las bslang ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)005:1403: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad bzhes shing bsnams su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1405: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK016(ma)005:1406: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams dga' ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)005:1407: a la la hoh zhen cing chags pa'i mtha' la nyon mongs rno skams gzir ba yis //
NK016(ma)005:1408: myong byed bde mchog brgyad dang ldan pas thabs kyi sku la smre bar mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:1409: 'gro kun tshangs par spyod pa'i byang chub sgo mor lam gtod cig /
NK016(ma)005:1410: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa'i tshogs la bka' stsol cig /
NK016(ma)005:1411: a la la hoh zhes pas dang pos lha rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK016(ma)005:1412: gnyis pas nyan thos rnams 'gog pa las bslang /
NK016(ma)005:1413: gsum pas rgyal sras rnams gzhan don la bskur bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1414: bdun pa rak+ta'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1416: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK016(ma)005:1417: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi rang bzhin du //
NK016(ma)005:1418: khams gsum dug gsum bsgral pa'i rak+ta mchog /
NK016(ma)005:1419: zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK016(ma)005:1420: khams gsum zil gnon dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1421: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:1422: badz+ra kro d+ha man+da la ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:1423: brgyad pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1425: chos dbyings rnam dag gtor gzhong rgya chen du //
NK016(ma)005:1426: gtor ma ye shes snang ba rgya mtshor 'khyil //
NK016(ma)005:1427: dkar dmar thig le bdud rtsis rol mtshor spel //
NK016(ma)005:1428: 'dod yon lha mo'i sprin gyis brgyan pa 'di //
NK016(ma)005:1429: zhi khro rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK016(ma)005:1430: +aahmh'u su ra te u ba b+h+yahka ma la m+aa
NK016(ma)005:1431: la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha
NK016(ma)005:1432: b+ha ga w+aan dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh
NK016(ma)005:1433: zhes dang / badz+ra kro d+ha man+dala ma h+aa ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:1434: zhes lan gsum gyis phul bas 'dod yon drug gi
NK016(ma)005:1435: lha mo mkha' khyab tu spros pa dkyil 'khor pa
NK016(ma)005:1436: rnams kyi dbang po drug gi gnas su thim pas
NK016(ma)005:1437: dgyes shing tshim par byas nas gnyis med du gyur
NK016(ma)005:1438: par bsam mo // dgu pa yid byung gi mchod pa ni //
NK016(ma)005:1439: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK016(ma)005:1440: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1441: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK016(ma)005:1442: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:1443: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK016(ma)005:1444: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK016(ma)005:1446: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK016(ma)005:1447: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK016(ma)005:1448: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK016(ma)005:1449: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK016(ma)005:1450: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK016(ma)005:1451: don shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK016(ma)005:1452: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK016(ma)005:1453: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK016(ma)005:1454: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1455: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1456: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK016(ma)005:1457: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK016(ma)005:1458: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK016(ma)005:1459: rin gyis yang na cig car du //
NK016(ma)005:1460: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK016(ma)005:1461: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK016(ma)005:1462: zhes pa'i tshig gis ji ltar ston pa'i mchod pa rnams mkha' khyab tu sprul te dbul lo //
NK016(ma)005:1464: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas ram dpag tu med pa chad /
NK016(ma)005:1466: ram las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas sems can
NK016(ma)005:1467: thams cad kyi snying nang na gnas pa'i rigs drug
NK016(ma)005:1468: gi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa bsregs /
NK016(ma)005:1469: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su spar bar bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)005:1471: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK016(ma)005:1472: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK016(ma)005:1473: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK016(ma)005:1474: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK016(ma)005:1475: bcu gcig pa sbyor mchod ni /
NK016(ma)005:1476: rang dang dkyil 'khor pa'i lha yab yum thams cad kyi mkha' gsang /
NK016(ma)005:1480: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)005:1481: dzahmh'u bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha sam rjes su
NK016(ma)005:1482: chags pa'i sbyor bas snyoms par zhugs te byang chub
NK016(ma)005:1483: kyi sems sprin spro bsdu'i sbyor bas bde ba chen
NK016(ma)005:1484: po'i ye shes mchog tu rgyas pa la blo bzhag
NK016(ma)005:1486: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)005:1487: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK016(ma)005:1488: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK016(ma)005:1489: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK016(ma)005:1490: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:1492: bcu gnyis pa 'dod yon ro mnyam gyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1494: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK016(ma)005:1495: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK016(ma)005:1497: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK016(ma)005:1498: 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mor dag pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:1499: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad bde ba chen por ro gcig tu gyur par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1500: bcu gsum pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:1502: bla med mchog gi mchod par sbyar ba 'di //
NK016(ma)005:1503: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK016(ma)005:1504: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK016(ma)005:1505: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1506: zhes pas mchod pa'i rol mo ji snyed pa thams
NK016(ma)005:1507: cad kyis 'khor gsum ye shes su dag pa mngon
NK016(ma)005:1508: du byas nas / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK016(ma)005:1509: h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa lpa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK016(ma)005:1510: du byas nas / / zhes nga rgyal bya zhing rol mo ye shes kyi sgras bskul lo //
NK016(ma)005:1511: bcu bzhi pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni //
NK016(ma)005:1512: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yis //
NK016(ma)005:1513: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1514: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:1515: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:1517: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1518: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK016(ma)005:1519: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK016(ma)005:1520: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1522: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK016(ma)005:1523: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:1524: ye shes lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK016(ma)005:1525: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1527: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK016(ma)005:1528: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs spro //
NK016(ma)005:1529: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK016(ma)005:1530: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po //
NK016(ma)005:1532: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK016(ma)005:1533: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK016(ma)005:1534: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1535: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK016(ma)005:1537: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)005:1538: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK016(ma)005:1539: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK016(ma)005:1540: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1541: hoh zhes pas zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:1543: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK016(ma)005:1545: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK016(ma)005:1546: mche ba zangs yag za byed che //
NK016(ma)005:1548: rngams pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK016(ma)005:1549: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK016(ma)005:1550: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK016(ma)005:1551: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che //
NK016(ma)005:1553: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK016(ma)005:1554: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK016(ma)005:1556: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1558: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK016(ma)005:1561: sna tshogs khros pas thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1563: bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK016(ma)005:1564: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms //
NK016(ma)005:1566: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che //
NK016(ma)005:1568: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK016(ma)005:1569: rdo rje chu ste sdud chen po //
NK016(ma)005:1570: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK016(ma)005:1571: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che /
NK016(ma)005:1572: hoh zhes pas khro bo ste /
NK016(ma)005:1573: chos nyid kyi rang sgra bstod dbyangs rgya mtsho'i rol mor kun tu sgrog par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1574: gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1576: hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na /
NK016(ma)005:1577: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das /
NK016(ma)005:1578: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi bye
NK016(ma)005:1579: brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje
NK016(ma)005:1580: sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs
NK016(ma)005:1581: pa rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum gyi dbyings na rnam
NK016(ma)005:1582: par bzhugs pa sems dpa'i tshogs sems ma'i 'khor /
NK016(ma)005:1583: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)005:1587: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK016(ma)005:1588: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK016(ma)005:1589: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK016(ma)005:1590: dam tshig gnyan po ma nor bar mnos pa las /
NK016(ma)005:1591: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag dang 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK016(ma)005:1592: lha nye bar ma bsgoms pa /
NK016(ma)005:1593: snying po dag par ma bgrangs pa /
NK016(ma)005:1594: sbyor ba mang po'i bar bskums pa /
NK016(ma)005:1595: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK016(ma)005:1596: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK016(ma)005:1597: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK016(ma)005:1598: dam rdzas lag len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK016(ma)005:1601: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK016(ma)005:1602: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur cing /
NK016(ma)005:1603: sems can gyi spyod pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:1604: khyad par du sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK016(ma)005:1605: khyad par gyi dam tshig gnyan po mngon par mnos pa las /
NK016(ma)005:1606: nyams shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa
NK016(ma)005:1607: thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis
NK016(ma)005:1608: mthol zhing bshags par mchis na /
NK016(ma)005:1609: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gis sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas /
NK016(ma)005:1610: tshangs pa mchog yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK016(ma)005:1611: bzhi pa dngos grub gsol ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1612: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK016(ma)005:1618: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs kyi bla
NK016(ma)005:1619: man chad nas dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rigs
NK016(ma)005:1620: brgyud gang lags pa thams cad phyi mar bsdad mi
NK016(ma)005:1621: 'tshal bar dus da lta nyid du thob par stsal
NK016(ma)005:1622: du gsol / rnal 'byor pa la bar du gcod par byed pa /
NK016(ma)005:1630: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang ltas ngan pa /
NK016(ma)005:1631: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir bzlog
NK016(ma)005:1632: cing ming tsam yang mi grags par zhi ba chen
NK016(ma)005:1634: gal te zhi bas bsgyur du mi btub pa zhig
NK016(ma)005:1635: mchis na yang drag po'i phrin las kyis dbang du
NK016(ma)005:1636: bsdu ba dang / gzir zhing mnan pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:1637: bsgral zhing spar ba la sogs te /
NK016(ma)005:1638: phrin las drag thabs rnam bzhis ji ltar 'dul ba
NK016(ma)005:1639: 'tshams pa bzhin mdzad nas ming tsam yang mi grags
NK016(ma)005:1641: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)005:1642: bcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK016(ma)005:1643: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK016(ma)005:1644: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:1645: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK016(ma)005:1646: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:1647: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK016(ma)005:1648: re smon thams can dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1650: lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1652: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK016(ma)005:1653: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:1654: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK016(ma)005:1655: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)005:1656: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK016(ma)005:1657: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK016(ma)005:1658: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK016(ma)005:1659: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlobs mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:1661: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK016(ma)005:1662: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK016(ma)005:1664: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:1668: skabs kyi 'jug bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK016(ma)005:1670: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal btab nas /
NK016(ma)005:1671: b+h+r+au bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dzahmh'u s+w+aa +aam h+aam
NK016(ma)005:1672: phata dzah h'u ha he phata b+h+yo ram phata dzah
NK016(ma)005:1673: zhes brjod pas / dam tshig 'khor lo las ye
NK016(ma)005:1674: shes kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa
NK016(ma)005:1675: logs su phye nas mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri
NK016(ma)005:1676: 'dabs 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1678: bdag mdun gyi lha rnams kyi thugs kar rang rang
NK016(ma)005:1679: gi phyag 'tshan sa bon gyis mtshan par bzla bya'i
NK016(ma)005:1680: sngags kyis bskor bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1682: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod
NK016(ma)005:1683: pa'i tshul du spros pas ye shes kyi lha tshogs
NK016(ma)005:1686: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK016(ma)005:1687: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pas bdag la
NK016(ma)005:1688: stsal zhing thim par dmigs la /
NK016(ma)005:1689: dam ye 'phro 'du ste gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang nas skyon bcu spangs te /
NK016(ma)005:1691: kun bzang sogs zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:1692: che mchog sogs khro bo so so'i bskyed sngags rnams
NK016(ma)005:1693: gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar te ji ltar rigs pa
NK016(ma)005:1694: bzlas nas / bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha
NK016(ma)005:1695: dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu +aah zhes zhi ba spyi'i sngags
NK016(ma)005:1696: bzlas nas / dang / ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:1697: ces khro bo spyi'i sngags re ci nus su bazla'o //
NK016(ma)005:1698: ting nge 'dzin la blo goms pa dag gis ni dzapa khang dbye ba'am ma dbye bar rung ste /
NK016(ma)005:1699: lus bsgul bskyod thams cad lha'i phyag rgya /
NK016(ma)005:1700: ngag rlung gi 'byung 'jug thams cad sngags kyi sgra gdangs /
NK016(ma)005:1701: sems dran rtog thams cad chos nyid byang chub sems kyi ngo bor rtogs pas bazla'o //
NK016(ma)005:1702: gsum pa skabs kyi 'jug bsdu ba la /
NK016(ma)005:1705: dzapa khang bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK016(ma)005:1708: yang na zhi khro'i gzhi bstod gnyis sbrel nas bya zhing /
NK016(ma)005:1710: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)005:1711: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK016(ma)005:1712: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa'i lha //
NK016(ma)005:1713: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)005:1716: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK016(ma)005:1717: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK016(ma)005:1718: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK016(ma)005:1719: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK016(ma)005:1720: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK016(ma)005:1721: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK016(ma)005:1722: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK016(ma)005:1723: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1724: zhes bzlas pa'i nyes byas su gyur pa rnams bshags /
NK016(ma)005:1726: dam ye'i dkyil 'khor rang bzhin dbyer med du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK016(ma)005:1728: zhes sogs kyis rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba sngar bzhin byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:1730: zhes brjod pas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la gnyis med du thim /
NK016(ma)005:1732: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes pas
NK016(ma)005:1733: gsal brtan dbang du byas nas yi ge brgya ba'ang
NK016(ma)005:1734: bazla'o // bzhi pa dbang don gyi dkyil 'khor spro ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1735: sngar bshams pa'i bum pa gnyis kro d+h+ai sh+aa r+ais bsang /
NK016(ma)005:1737: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+au yig gnyis chad /
NK016(ma)005:1738: bum pa so so'i nang du song ba yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)005:1739: rin po che'i bum pa yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK016(ma)005:1745: lha'i gos kyis mgul bcings pa /
NK016(ma)005:1746: dpag bsam shing gi kha rgyan can /
NK016(ma)005:1747: nang chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis yongs su gang
NK016(ma)005:1748: ba'i rnam rgyal bum pa'i nang du 'khor lo ser
NK016(ma)005:1749: po rtsibs bzhi pa sgo bzhi glo 'bur gyi tshul
NK016(ma)005:1750: du gnas pa'i dbus su seng ge /
NK016(ma)005:1752: lhor rta mchog nub tu rma bya /
NK016(ma)005:1753: byang du shang shang gis btegs pa'i rin po che'i
NK016(ma)005:1754: khri sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan
NK016(ma)005:1755: lnga'i steng du / slar yang rang gi thugs ka nas /
NK016(ma)005:1766: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams dang bcas par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:1770: dbus su mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)005:1771: dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dril
NK016(ma)005:1772: bu dang rdo rje 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor
NK016(ma)005:1775: shar du rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril
NK016(ma)005:1776: bu spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo'i dril bu dang
NK016(ma)005:1779: lhor rin 'byung ser po rin po che dang dril
NK016(ma)005:1780: bu m+aa ma k+ai ser mo rin po che'i dril
NK016(ma)005:1784: nub tu snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu
NK016(ma)005:1785: gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma'i dril bu dang pad+ma
NK016(ma)005:1787: t+aam badz+ra ra ti byang du don grub ljang gu
NK016(ma)005:1788: ral gri dang dril bu dam tshig sgrol ma ljang
NK016(ma)005:1789: gu ral gri'i dril bu dang ral gri 'dzin pa
NK016(ma)005:1791: yab rnams mnyam pa'i skyil krung dang yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:1792: zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing tshul dgus brjid pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:1793: khrus bum gyi nang du pad+ma 'dab ma brgya pa'i
NK016(ma)005:1794: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su a yig dkar po dri
NK016(ma)005:1795: ma med pa zla ba ltar gsal ba las rigs
NK016(ma)005:1796: brgya'i rang bzhin yi ge'i sprin phyungs nas pad+ma'i 'dab
NK016(ma)005:1797: ma dang po nas brtsams te rim pa bzhin 'khor
NK016(ma)005:1798: pa ni / badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya /
NK016(ma)005:1800: badz+ra sa t+wa t+we no pa tisha tha dri d+d+ho me b+ha wa /
NK016(ma)005:1803: a nu raka to me b+ha wa /
NK016(ma)005:1804: sara ba sida d+hi me pra yatsa tsha sara ba
NK016(ma)005:1805: kara ma su tsa me tsita tam sh+re yahku ru
NK016(ma)005:1806: h'u / ha ha ha ha hoh b+ha ga w+aan
NK016(ma)005:1807: sara ba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra m+aa me munya
NK016(ma)005:1808: tsa badz+ri b+ha wa ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+wa
NK016(ma)005:1809: h'u / +aa / zhes pa rnams mu tig gi phreng ba lta bur gsal bar gyur /
NK016(ma)005:1810: s+pha sam badz+ra sat+wa ah dbus su dpal rdo rje
NK016(ma)005:1811: sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK016(ma)005:1812: pa / zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan dpe'i lang tshor rab tu rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)005:1813: g.yas rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK016(ma)005:1814: dar gyi na bza' dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)005:1815: seng ges btegs pa'i khri pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la sems dpa'i skyil krung gis rol pa /
NK016(ma)005:1816: khor yug gi yi ge'i phreng ba rnams kyang zhi
NK016(ma)005:1817: khro rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i rnam pa can
NK016(ma)005:1818: du bkra lam gyis gsal bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1819: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK016(ma)005:1820: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis byin gyis brlab /
NK016(ma)005:1821: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK016(ma)005:1822: e h+ye his ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)005:1823: dzahmh'u bam ham hohs gnyis med du bstim /
NK016(ma)005:1824: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK016(ma)005:1829: chos sku nam mkha' ma dang /
NK016(ma)005:1831: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)005:1832: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)005:1833: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)005:1834: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)005:1835: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo zhes sogs kyis bstod nas /
NK016(ma)005:1836: bdag gi snying ga nas sngags gyi phreng ba gzungs thag la 'khril te song bas /
NK016(ma)005:1837: bum pa'i lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)005:1838: snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang sems ye shes kyi bdud rtsir babs pas bum pa gang bar bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)005:1839: dbang bum la dmigs nas zhi ba rigs lnga so so'i sngags dang /
NK016(ma)005:1840: spyi sngags po d+hi tsit+ta brgya rtsa sogs bzlas la /
NK016(ma)005:1841: slar yang khro bo rigs lnga'i bskyed sngags rnams brjod pas /
NK016(ma)005:1842: zhi ba rigs lnga khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum gyi skur gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1843: khro bo rigs lnga'i sngags so so dang /
NK016(ma)005:1844: spyi sngags ru lu yang ci nus bzla zhing /
NK016(ma)005:1845: dmigs pa snga ma lta bus khrus bum la dmigs
NK016(ma)005:1846: te ye ge brgya pa ci nus su bzlas nas
NK016(ma)005:1847: / gtso bo'i sngags kyis thod chu phul bas /
NK016(ma)005:1848: lha thams cad chags pa chen pos ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)005:1849: bdud rtsir zhu ba bum chu dang ro gcig tu
NK016(ma)005:1851: spyir lugs 'di la bum sgrub rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:1852: dang dbyer med du mdzad nas logs su mi mdzad
NK016(ma)005:1853: pa'ang yod mod / zur du byas phyin tshul 'di
NK016(ma)005:1854: dbang bum du dmigs phyed pa'i rnam pa gsal ba
NK016(ma)005:1855: pa'ang yod mod / dang / rtsa ba'i yi ge'i don la yang 'byor bar sems so //
NK016(ma)005:1856: 'dir las sbyor gyi bzlas pa byas na skabs su bab bar 'gyur te /
NK016(ma)005:1858: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi zhal nas sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK016(ma)005:1859: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'phros pas khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas /
NK016(ma)005:1861: dmigs yul gtso bor gyur pa'i sems can thams cad sangs rgyas zhing du bsgral bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:1862: yi ge brgya pa spel tshig can brgya rtsa sogs bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)005:1863: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi yang snying yi ge brgya pa zhes bya ba /
NK016(ma)005:1864: nyams chag dang rtog sgrib thams cad sbyong bar byed pa 'di bzlas pas /
NK016(ma)005:1868: bag chags ngan pa can khyed rnams kyi nyams chag thams cad skongs te /
NK016(ma)005:1869: ngan song du ltung ba'i las kyi sgrib pa las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)005:1870: tshe 'di la yang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras
NK016(ma)005:1871: kyi dam par dgongs nas bsrung zhing skyob bar mdzad
NK016(ma)005:1872: la / shi 'phos nas kyang bde bar gshegs pa
NK016(ma)005:1873: rnams kyi sras kyi thu bor 'gyur bar gdon mi
NK016(ma)005:1874: la / za'o // zhes gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:1875: lnga pa bskang ba bya ba la bdun las /
NK016(ma)005:1877: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku
NK016(ma)005:1878: chen po'i klong du 'khor 'das ro mnyam par bltas
NK016(ma)005:1880: bskang ngo kalpasa thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1881: dngos po stong nyid klong du bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1882: snang ba ye shes klong du bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1883: gsal ba shes rab klong sdug bsngal chos nyid klong
NK016(ma)005:1884: skye ba med pa'i dbyings su 'gag pa med pa'i
NK016(ma)005:1885: mkha' la skye 'gag gnyis med klong du nyams chag
NK016(ma)005:1887: dbang dang dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:1888: gnyis pa bdud rtsis bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1890: bskang ngo bdud rtsis thugs dam kun gzhi klong yangs b+hany+dza ru //
NK016(ma)005:1891: byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis bkang //
NK016(ma)005:1892: 'di yang rang byung bdud rtsi ste //
NK016(ma)005:1893: dmigs med chos sku'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1894: gdangs gsal 'bar ye shes sgrib med 'di yang longs
NK016(ma)005:1895: spyod rdzogs sku'i mchog gi 'od gsal thig le 'bar
NK016(ma)005:1896: ba'i 'di yang rgyal ba sprul sku'i ye shes rtsa
NK016(ma)005:1897: lnga'i skye med a dkar 'di yang zhi ba'i lha
NK016(ma)005:1898: tshogs dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i shes rab rang gsal 'di
NK016(ma)005:1899: yang khro bo'i lha tshogs bdud rtsi sman gyi dam
NK016(ma)005:1900: tshig 'dis // mchod 'os rgya mtsho'i thugs nyams chag
NK016(ma)005:1901: dbang dang ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi
NK016(ma)005:1902: tshig 'dis // / zhes brjod la rol mo'i bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:1903: gsum pa gtor mas bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1905: bskang ngo gtor mas b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i gtor gzhong du //
NK016(ma)005:1906: shangs kyi rlung sgrom dpal bshos btsugs //
NK016(ma)005:1908: sgron ma mig gi dza gad stsal //
NK016(ma)005:1909: dbang po lnga yi rak+tasa brgyan //
NK016(ma)005:1910: 'di yang rang byung gtor ma ste //
NK016(ma)005:1911: bla ma rig 'dzin mchog gsum dang //
NK016(ma)005:1912: zhi khro rab 'byams thugs nyi zla kha sbyor tsit+ta
NK016(ma)005:1913: 'bar ba'i pad+ma 'dab brgyad rnam shes tshogs brgyad rtsa
NK016(ma)005:1914: chen bzhi yi 'di yang bla ma zhi khro khyab
NK016(ma)005:1915: brdal lpags pa'i rus pa rang snang rang snang sha
NK016(ma)005:1916: yi bkrag dang mdangs kyi khrag dang chu ser 'di
NK016(ma)005:1917: yang bla ma zhi khro khog pa stong pa'i mchin
NK016(ma)005:1918: pa rang snang glo mtsher mkhal ma'i gu h+ya nang
NK016(ma)005:1919: khrol rang snang mkhris pa'i 'di yang bla ma zhi
NK016(ma)005:1920: khro ba ling 'dod yon dam tshig 'dis //
NK016(ma)005:1921: mchos 'os nyams chag dbang dang ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:1923: bzhi pa rak+tasa bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1925: bskang ngo rak+tasa spyi bo bde chen b+hany+dza ru //
NK016(ma)005:1926: sdug bsngal rnam rtog rak+tasa bkang //
NK016(ma)005:1928: bla ma zhi khro mgrin pa longs spyod sna tshogs
NK016(ma)005:1929: yid kyi 'di yang bla ma zhi khro snying ga
NK016(ma)005:1930: chos kyi bsam pa blo yi 'di yang bla ma
NK016(ma)005:1931: zhi khro lte ba sprul pa'i nyon mongs srid rtsa'i
NK016(ma)005:1932: 'di yang bla ma zhi khro gsang ba bde skyong
NK016(ma)005:1933: bde ba thig le'i 'di yang bla ma zhi khro
NK016(ma)005:1934: rak+ta 'bar ba'i dam mchod 'os nyams chag dbang dang
NK016(ma)005:1937: lnga pa sgron mes bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1939: bskang ngo sgron mes brdal khyab lpags pa'i kong bu ru //
NK016(ma)005:1940: khrag dang chu ser mar khus gtams //
NK016(ma)005:1941: sha dang rus pa'i sdong bu la //
NK016(ma)005:1942: rang gsal bkrag mdangs zhun mar spar //
NK016(ma)005:1943: 'di yang rang byung sgron me ste //
NK016(ma)005:1944: bla ma zhi khro dung chen 'bar ba'i go ro
NK016(ma)005:1945: tsa na'i gsal byed rtsa lnga'i dbang po sgo lnga'i
NK016(ma)005:1946: 'di yang bla ma zhi khro tsit+ta 'bar ba'i snying
NK016(ma)005:1947: tshil dkar dmar pad+ma 'dab brgyad rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK016(ma)005:1948: 'di yang bla ma zhi khro a wa d+h+au ti'i
NK016(ma)005:1949: rang gsal 'od kyi 'khor lo bdun brtsegs byang chub
NK016(ma)005:1950: sems kyi 'di yang bla ma zhi khro mi shigs
NK016(ma)005:1951: thig le'i skye med ye shes rtsa phran bcu gnyis
NK016(ma)005:1952: rig pa rang byung 'di yang bla ma zhi khro
NK016(ma)005:1953: ye shes rtsa lnga'i a dkar rtsa gcig ye shes
NK016(ma)005:1954: 'od zer shes rab 'bru lnga'i 'di yang bla ma
NK016(ma)005:1955: zhi khro mchog gi 'od gsal gdangs gsal 'od kyi
NK016(ma)005:1956: thig le 'bar ba'i ye shes lnga yi 'di yang
NK016(ma)005:1957: bla ma zhi khro kun gzhi klong yangs chos kyi
NK016(ma)005:1958: dbyings kyi byang chub sems kyi sku lnga lhun grub
NK016(ma)005:1959: 'di yang bla ma zhi khro sgron ma 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)005:1960: dam tshig 'dis // mchod 'os nyams chag dbang dang d+ai pa pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1962: yam hohshud+d+he bam hoh lam hoh ram hoh a +aahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1963: chag nyams dang rtog sgrib thams cad sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:1964: zhes khrus bdun gyi rig pa lan bdun du bazla'o //
NK016(ma)005:1965: drug pa zhi ba gnas dag gis bskang ba ni //
NK016(ma)005:1966: yid kyi rnam shes gnas dag pa //
NK016(ma)005:1967: kun tu bzang po'i thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1968: chos kyi ngo bo gnas kun tu bzang mo'i phung
NK016(ma)005:1969: po lnga po gnas rgyal ba yab lnga'i 'byung ba
NK016(ma)005:1970: lnga po gnas rgyal ba yum lnga'i rnam shes tshogs
NK016(ma)005:1971: brgyad gnas sems dpa' brgyad kyi rnam shes yul brgyad
NK016(ma)005:1972: gnas sems ma brgyad kyi lus kyi chos bzhi gnas
NK016(ma)005:1973: khro bo bzhi yi rtag chad mu bzhi gnas khro
NK016(ma)005:1974: mo bzhi yi nyon mongs drug po gnas thub pa
NK016(ma)005:1976: bdun pa khro bo gnas gyur gyis bskang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:1978: kun gzhi yid chos gnas gyur pa dpal chen yab yum thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)005:1979: nyon mongs dug lnga gnas gyur khrag 'thung yab lnga'i
NK016(ma)005:1980: 'byung ba lus lnga gnas khrag 'thung yum lnga'i rnam
NK016(ma)005:1981: bzhi'i rtog pa gnas he ru ka bzhi'i skye gnas
NK016(ma)005:1982: bzhi po gnas kro d+h+ai rigs bzhi'i rnam 'gyur tshogs
NK016(ma)005:1983: brgyad gnas khro mo brgyad kyi rnam 'gyur yul brgyad
NK016(ma)005:1984: gnas phra men brgyad kyi rtag chad mtha' bzhi gnas
NK016(ma)005:1985: sgo ma bzhi yi sna tshogs rtog pa gnas dbang
NK016(ma)005:1986: mo nyer brgyad mi shigs sku yi thugs 'gag med
NK016(ma)005:1987: gsung gi 'gyur med thugs kyi yon tan mi zad
NK016(ma)005:1988: phrin las rgyan gyi ye shes 'khor lo'i thugs nyams
NK016(ma)005:1989: chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:1990: rtog sgrib thams cad dag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:1991: bskangs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)005:1992: zhes pas phyi nang gsang ba'i 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK016(ma)005:1993: thams cad 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)005:1994: dbyings su ro mnyam par bskang ngo //
NK016(ma)005:1995: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la lnga ste /
NK016(ma)005:2000: bsngo ba bya zhing shis pa brjod pa'o //
NK016(ma)005:2001: dang po tshogs mchod la 'ang lnga las /
NK016(ma)005:2002: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2003: dam rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad rnams bshams nas /
NK016(ma)005:2005: ram yam kham gis dngos 'dzin nyes skyon bsregs gtor bkrus te dag par byas /
NK016(ma)005:2007: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la h'u s+w+aa
NK016(ma)005:2008: +aam h+aa las bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK016(ma)005:2009: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi ro brgya pa 'dod yon
NK016(ma)005:2010: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK016(ma)005:2011: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK016(ma)005:2012: bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2013: yi ge gsum lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlab /
NK016(ma)005:2014: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2015: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK016(ma)005:2016: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK016(ma)005:2018: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2020: ru lu ru lu h'u e h+ye hi +aa na yu dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes pas spyan drangs la /
NK016(ma)005:2021: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga am ku sha dzahp+aa sha h'u /
NK016(ma)005:2023: g+han+de hoh zhes dgug gzhug bcing mnyes bya /
NK016(ma)005:2024: gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)005:2025: dang po spyiir mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2026: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au sogs bzhi bsnol dang /
NK016(ma)005:2027: h'u rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK016(ma)005:2028: sems dpa' sngon mo'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK016(ma)005:2029: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK016(ma)005:2030: badz+ra l+aa s+ya'i mchod par rol //
NK016(ma)005:2031: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga l+aa s+ya h'u /
NK016(ma)005:2034: mnyam pa nyid kyi badz+ra m+aa le'i m+aa le t+r+aam /
NK016(ma)005:2035: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK016(ma)005:2036: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK016(ma)005:2037: so sor rtog pa'i badz+ra g+airti'i g+air+t+ai h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi sdan ma //
NK016(ma)005:2039: bya ba nan tan badz+ra n+ri ti'i n+ri ti +aah zhes mchod /
NK016(ma)005:2040: gnyis pa khyad par gyi mchod pa la gsum las /
NK016(ma)005:2041: tshogs phud cha gsum mam bzhir spros la /
NK016(ma)005:2044: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK016(ma)005:2045: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK016(ma)005:2046: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK016(ma)005:2047: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2048: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
NK016(ma)005:2049: 'dod yon lha mos nam mkha' gang //
NK016(ma)005:2051: spyan sogs bde bas tshim gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2052: +aahmh'u su ra ta u pa b+h+yehk+aa ma ha h+ai
NK016(ma)005:2053: pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pas
NK016(ma)005:2057: dang por byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK016(ma)005:2058: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK016(ma)005:2059: sems can dbang gis nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK016(ma)005:2060: mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)005:2061: yi ge brgya pa'ang brjod cing 'khon gcugs dag par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:2063: ling+ga logs su ma bcas na tshogs phud tha ma
NK016(ma)005:2064: de'i 'dod yon gyi lha mo h'u zhes rang la
NK016(ma)005:2065: bsdus pa'am / sngar byin rlabs kyi gong du bcad na ni der zad la /
NK016(ma)005:2066: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:2067: bdag nyid rdo rje khro bo'i skur gyur /
NK016(ma)005:2069: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)005:2070: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2071: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2072: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2073: zhi khro sgyu 'phrul rnam par rol pa'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2074: sprul la yang sprul phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2075: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis ma rungs
NK016(ma)005:2076: pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa thams
NK016(ma)005:2077: cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par
NK016(ma)005:2078: gyur cig / n+ri yam dzahn+ri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah
NK016(ma)005:2079: tri yam dzahtri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes lcags kyu'i
NK016(ma)005:2081: dzahmh'u bam hohs dgug bcings bsdams nas myos par byas
NK016(ma)005:2082: te 'dug pa'i snying gar dwangs ma ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)005:2083: a dkar po dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)005:2084: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK016(ma)005:2086: gzas po'i snying ga'i sgo phye /
NK016(ma)005:2089: dug lnga ye shes su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)005:2090: dwangs ma sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lor spar te sangs rgyas par gyur /
NK016(ma)005:2091: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka m+aa ra badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu tra /
NK016(ma)005:2092: ma tam kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:2093: hri da ya pi pa h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:2094: snyigs ma rang snang sgyu 'phrul gyi 'khor lo khro
NK016(ma)005:2095: tshogs 'bar bas rdo rje bza' ba'i dam tshig tu
NK016(ma)005:2098: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK016(ma)005:2099: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2100: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)005:2101: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK016(ma)005:2103: sarba dush+tana m+aa ra ya h'u phata kyis ling+ga'i gnas
NK016(ma)005:2104: lngar phur bu btab pas bsad cing bcad gtubs khog
NK016(ma)005:2106: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK016(ma)005:2110: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kha le le le h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:2112: h'u sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2113: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK016(ma)005:2114: snying rje rjam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK016(ma)005:2115: sku yi dngos po shin tu sgyur pa yin //
NK016(ma)005:2116: gar yang sgrub po rnal 'byor las //
NK016(ma)005:2117: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK016(ma)005:2118: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK016(ma)005:2119: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2120: me tog sogs dang tsan+dana dri //
NK016(ma)005:2121: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2122: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK016(ma)005:2123: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK016(ma)005:2124: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK016(ma)005:2125: h'u dang phata gyi ldan par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2126: ces pas bsgral mtha' sbyor ba'i dam tshig chen por bsgrubs pas lha thams cad tshim par byas la /
NK016(ma)005:2128: zhes pas zhi bar nga rgyal 'phos te /
NK016(ma)005:2131: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK016(ma)005:2132: ston ka'i zla zhal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK016(ma)005:2133: bcom ldan bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK016(ma)005:2134: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK016(ma)005:2135: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngam pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK016(ma)005:2136: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:2137: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK016(ma)005:2138: bzhes te a la la yis dgyes par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2141: sa ma ya b+ha k+sha hu /
NK016(ma)005:2142: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK016(ma)005:2143: dzah h'u bam hoh pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes 'khor gsum bde ba chen por ro mnyam mo //
NK016(ma)005:2144: bzhi pa tshogs la rol ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2145: lnga pa lhag ma gtong ba ni bla ma rnams kyi phyag len la dbang gi mthar mdzad la /
NK016(ma)005:2146: chos skyong spyi sgos dang 'jig rten pa'i gtor ma
NK016(ma)005:2147: bsngo ba rnams ni 'dir byas na skabs su bab
NK016(ma)005:2148: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2149: cho ga'i don 'gangs che shos gcig yin pa'i phyir dngos gzhi'i khongs su bsdebs nas /
NK016(ma)005:2150: tshogs mchod man chad rjes kyi rtsis 'gos bsdus na'ang legs mod kyi /
NK016(ma)005:2152: de ltar na gong ma'i phyag len bzhin 'dir bya ste /
NK016(ma)005:2153: de la bdag nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2154: gzhan la dbang bskur ba gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)005:2156: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK016(ma)005:2157: tha mi dad pa dbang len pa'i yul du byas
NK016(ma)005:2158: nas / dbang gi bya ba rnams gtso bo las
NK016(ma)005:2159: phye ba'i rgyal thebs kyis mdzad pas mos te dbang
NK016(ma)005:2161: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang rang bzhin dbyer
NK016(ma)005:2162: med du bsgoms nas rig pa'i me tog dor ba
NK016(ma)005:2163: nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'ang yin pas
NK016(ma)005:2164: / gzhan la dbang bskur dang 'brel na phyi ma dang /
NK016(ma)005:2165: ma 'brel na snga ma ltar byas pas gnas skabs su spros pa 'tshams par 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2167: de gnyis gang gi mthar yang dkyil 'khor la thal mo sbyor bas btud de //
NK016(ma)005:2168: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:2169: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)005:2172: zhes gsol bas gnang ba byin par bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:2173: gnyis pa slob mar dbang bskur ba la gsum gyi /
NK016(ma)005:2174: dang po 'jug pa la dgu las /
NK016(ma)005:2175: dang po khrus sogs bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2176: dkyil 'khor khang pa'i phyi rol du khrus byas /
NK016(ma)005:2180: +aa kham w+ai ra h'u gis me tog gtad /
NK016(ma)005:2181: gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2182: kye ma kyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)005:2183: 'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyobs shig /
NK016(ma)005:2184: dbang mchog rgyal po bsgrag tu gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2185: slad nas mi 'chab mi sbed do //
NK016(ma)005:2187: gsum pa snang ba byin pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2188: bu 'dir shog cig rigs kyi bu //
NK016(ma)005:2189: rang gi nyams dang zlas nyams kyis //
NK016(ma)005:2190: na rag gnas su ltung ba las //
NK016(ma)005:2191: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK016(ma)005:2192: zhes brjod la yol ba'i nang du drang /
NK016(ma)005:2194: nyes byas la bshags sdom gyi bsam pa drag pos /
NK016(ma)005:2195: kye ma kyi hud bdag 'dra bas //
NK016(ma)005:2196: las ngan rnam smin myong 'gyur na //
NK016(ma)005:2197: nyes byas 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)005:2198: mgon po'i thugs rjes bdag sgrol cig /
NK016(ma)005:2199: lnga pa sems bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK016(ma)005:2201: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)005:2204: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK016(ma)005:2206: drug pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2207: sngar gtad pa'i me tog thal mos bzung ste /
NK016(ma)005:2209: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)005:2210: rin chen me tog 'di dor bas //
NK016(ma)005:2211: rnam par dag pa'i las gang gis //
NK016(ma)005:2212: thugs rje mnyes par 'gyid mdzad lha //
NK016(ma)005:2213: gang yin de la 'bab par shog /
NK016(ma)005:2215: pra ti sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:2216: bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:2217: zhes slob dpon gyi sku la 'dor du bcug nas
NK016(ma)005:2218: dbu la sogs pa sku'i gnas so so dang nye
NK016(ma)005:2219: ring las mtshon te mchog dang rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK016(ma)005:2220: dngos grub las 'di 'grub par 'gyur zhes brda sprad
NK016(ma)005:2221: / bdun pa me tog gi dbang ni /
NK016(ma)005:2223: dam tshig bden pa chen po'i mthu //
NK016(ma)005:2224: sngon sbyangs las kyis 'brel ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2225: gnyis su med pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK016(ma)005:2226: mnyam par byin rlabs mdzad du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2227: h'u badz+ra sa t+wa a be sha ya +aah zhes me tog gi phreng ba mgo bor bcing /
NK016(ma)005:2228: brgyad pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2230: ji ltar mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK016(ma)005:2231: ma rig ldongs pa bsal ba ltar //
NK016(ma)005:2232: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs kyi lhas //
NK016(ma)005:2233: skal ldan bu khyod mig dabye'o //
NK016(ma)005:2234: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)005:2235: ces pas mig dbye zhing gdong g.yogs dgrol /
NK016(ma)005:2236: dgu pa mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2238: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK016(ma)005:2239: khyod ni sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK016(ma)005:2240: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs //
NK016(ma)005:2241: dngos grub thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:2242: dam tshig mchog tu khyod 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2244: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro rab 'byams kyi dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:2245: chen po rten dang brten par bcas pa thams cad
NK016(ma)005:2246: mngon sum bzhin du mthong bar bsam mo //
NK016(ma)005:2247: gnyis pa dbang gi dngos gzhi la /
NK016(ma)005:2248: sbyor ba sdig sgrib dag byed dang /
NK016(ma)005:2249: dngos gzhi yon tan yar 'phel gyi dbang gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)005:2252: slob ma khrus sa'i stan la bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)005:2253: thugs ka nas spros pa'i khrod pa'i tshogs dang /
NK016(ma)005:2254: bi shwa badz+ra gyi sngags brjod pas bgegs rnams bskrad
NK016(ma)005:2255: bar bsam la yungs thun gyis brab pa sogs bya'o
NK016(ma)005:2257: slob bus tshe rabs thogs ma med pa nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad gsang gnas su du /
NK016(ma)005:2259: snying gar pre rnams kyi rnams par gnas pa'i so
NK016(ma)005:2260: so'i steng du rig pa'i ye shes ram yam kham
NK016(ma)005:2261: gsum du gsal bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2262: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum bskul /
NK016(ma)005:2263: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas gsang gnas kyi du bsregs gtor sbyangs par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2265: yam s+pha ra kham s+pha ra ces sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:2267: slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga
NK016(ma)005:2268: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h'u
NK016(ma)005:2269: s+w+aa +aam h+aa / g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la
NK016(ma)005:2270: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du m+aum l+aam
NK016(ma)005:2271: m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan pa rnams rigs lnga
NK016(ma)005:2272: yab yum bcur gyur par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2275: badz+ra any+tsa li sa sor mo bsnol /
NK016(ma)005:2277: zhes bsdams pas rigs lnga yab yum mnyam par sbyor bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2278: bden pa'i stobs brjod cing thal mo dkrol nas /
NK016(ma)005:2279: na ra ka shud+d+ha tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)005:2280: ces brjod cing thal mo dkrugs pas /
NK016(ma)005:2281: slob dpon gyi thugs ka dang rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams
NK016(ma)005:2282: nas 'od zer 'phros pas dmyal bar skye ba'i sa
NK016(ma)005:2283: bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs par bsam mo
NK016(ma)005:2285: sngon las la 'gyod cing bshags sdom gyi bsam pas /
NK016(ma)005:2286: kye ma gyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)005:2287: zhes sogs kyi gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)005:2289: bu 'dir shog cig rang gi na rag gnas skyob phyir zhes dbang stegs su drangs /
NK016(ma)005:2291: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)005:2295: khrus bum gyis dbang bskur la /
NK016(ma)005:2296: til gyi gong bu bzhin gang ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:2297: rgyal bas bum pa bzung nas ni //
NK016(ma)005:2298: 'di nyid du ni blugs mdzad pas //
NK016(ma)005:2299: bag chags ma lus dag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2302: da ha da ha sogs btags pa brjod bzhin du bkrus nas /
NK016(ma)005:2303: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi
NK016(ma)005:2304: sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad sh+ain+tam ku
NK016(ma)005:2307: de bzhin du sa bcad gnyis pa man chad kyi
NK016(ma)005:2308: sgos chos bye brag pa rnams 'don pa spos nas
NK016(ma)005:2309: bya ste / slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od dang ram yam kham gis snying ga'i pre sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:2311: pre ta tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)005:2312: yi dwags su skye ba'i sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:2313: kye ma kyi hud kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)005:2314: bu 'dir sogs kyi rkang pa gsum pa /
NK016(ma)005:2315: pre ta' gnas su ltung ba las /
NK016(ma)005:2317: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka ga te he t+aum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)005:2319: khrus bum gyis sngar bzhin bkru ba las /
NK016(ma)005:2321: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi sgo nas bsags pa'i zhes sbyar /
NK016(ma)005:2323: thugs ka'i 'od dang ram yam kham gis lte ba'i tre sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:2325: tir+ya ka ga te tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)005:2326: dud 'gror skye ba'i sa non bag chags dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK016(ma)005:2327: kye ma kyi hud kyis gsol ba gdab /
NK016(ma)005:2328: dud 'gro'i gnas su ltung ba las /
NK016(ma)005:2330: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga ta he tum h'u phata /
NK016(ma)005:2332: khrus bum gyis sngar bzhin bkru ba las /
NK016(ma)005:2334: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi sgo nas bsags pa'i zhes sbyar ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2335: bskabs 'dir rnam snang dang mi 'khrugs pa'i gzungs sngags
NK016(ma)005:2336: bzla ba'ang bla ma rnams kyi phyag len gyi rgyun
NK016(ma)005:2337: la snang bas de ltar yang bya zhing /
NK016(ma)005:2339: rigs kyi bus tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa
NK016(ma)005:2340: nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib nyon mongs bag chags skal
NK016(ma)005:2341: ba ngan pa dang bkra mi shis pa'i dngos po
NK016(ma)005:2342: thams cad nye bar zhi ste shin tu bkra shis
NK016(ma)005:2343: par gyur cig / ces brjod do //
NK016(ma)005:2344: de dag ni ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)005:2345: bcud khyad par can blug pa la sngon du snod dag par byed pa bzhin no //
NK016(ma)005:2346: gnyis pa yon tan yar 'phel gyi dbang bskur ba la bzhi las /
NK016(ma)005:2347: dang po rdo rje sems dpa'i bum pa'i dbang gis lus kyi dri ma sbyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2348: slob ma seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK016(ma)005:2349: sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du
NK016(ma)005:2350: rdo rje sems dpa' yum dang bcas pa'i rnam pas
NK016(ma)005:2352: ye shes rgyal po sogs kyis gsol ba btab par gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)005:2353: slob dpon gyis rnam par rgyal ba'i bum pa spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK016(ma)005:2354: sku gsum dam tshig las byung ba //
NK016(ma)005:2355: nyon mongs zhe sngang mjoms pa yis //
NK016(ma)005:2356: lha yi bdud rtsi dag pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)005:2357: mi bskyod pa ru dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2358: ma h+aa sh+aunya t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)005:2359: zhes bum chu spyi bor gtigs pas /
NK016(ma)005:2360: mi bskyod pa'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur /
NK016(ma)005:2362: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)005:2363: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)005:2364: mi bskyod pa sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu
NK016(ma)005:2366: de lta na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi zhe sdang dag /
NK016(ma)005:2367: rnam par shes pa'i phung po mi bskyod par gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)005:2368: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)005:2370: de bzhin du rna ltag g.yas su bum chu gtigs la /
NK016(ma)005:2371: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid che //
NK016(ma)005:2372: ser sna'i rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)005:2373: rtag tu chags med sbyin pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)005:2374: rdzogs sangs rgyas su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2375: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa rin 'byung gi rang bzhin
NK016(ma)005:2376: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes 'khyil ba las rin
NK016(ma)005:2378: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan mnyam pa
NK016(ma)005:2379: nyid kyi ye shes zhes sogs kyi khyad par ma
NK016(ma)005:2380: gtogs sngar ltar shes par byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:2381: ltag par bum chu sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK016(ma)005:2382: mi phyed rdo rje gsang ba las //
NK016(ma)005:2384: rdo rje chos su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2385: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na snang ba mtha' yas
NK016(ma)005:2386: kyi rang bzhin so sor rtog pa'i ye shes snang
NK016(ma)005:2388: 'du shes phung po snang ba mtha' yas so sor
NK016(ma)005:2389: rtog pa'i ye shes rna ltag g.yon du bum chu
NK016(ma)005:2390: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK016(ma)005:2391: 'gro don mnyam pa med pa yis //
NK016(ma)005:2392: phrag dog rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)005:2393: gnyis su med par dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2394: ma h+aa kri t+ya don yod grub pa'i rang bzhin
NK016(ma)005:2395: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes don grub phrag dog
NK016(ma)005:2396: dag / 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub
NK016(ma)005:2397: par bya ba grub pa'i ye shes bum chu dpral
NK016(ma)005:2398: bar rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)005:2399: gti mug rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)005:2400: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:2401: rdo rje'i ming du rab tu grags //
NK016(ma)005:2402: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang
NK016(ma)005:2403: bzhin me long lta bu'i ye shes rnam snang gti
NK016(ma)005:2404: mug dag / gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang
NK016(ma)005:2405: mdzad du me long lta bu'i ye shes zhes rtogs
NK016(ma)005:2406: mug dag / pa bskyed / skabs su bab na dbu rgyan bcing ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2407: rdor dril gtod pa rnams byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:2408: de dang de'i mthar chus kyang dbang bskur ba sngar ltar bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:2409: de'i mthar sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2410: sku'am phyag mtshan nam phyag rgya gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK016(ma)005:2411: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK016(ma)005:2413: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:2414: zhes pa'i bar gzhan sngar dang 'dra ba las sngags tshan so so'i gong du /
NK016(ma)005:2415: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK016(ma)005:2416: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi sku //
NK016(ma)005:2417: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)005:2418: sku yi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2420: gsung dang thugs kyang de bzhin du bsgyur bas so //
NK016(ma)005:2421: de ltar slob ma mchod pa'i yul du gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)005:2424: bzhi bsnol gyis mchod par bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:2425: gnyis pa mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i dbang gis gsang ba'i ye shes byin dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2427: rkang rting sprad nas rtse mo btsugs /
NK016(ma)005:2429: lag gnyis gru mo phyir brgyangs pas spyi bor gtor ma bzung /
NK016(ma)005:2430: rtsa dang nywa bzhi grim gyis sgrim pa ni lus kyi las so //
NK016(ma)005:2432: sarba r+au pa ba lim ta ph+au dza kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:2434: gang shar rtsol med du klod la smrar gzhug /
NK016(ma)005:2435: sems kyi las snod kyi 'jig rten b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)005:2436: gtor gzhong du rgya tshad med pa'i zla ba la
NK016(ma)005:2437: gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can thams cad kyi lus
NK016(ma)005:2438: dang longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)005:2439: thams cad / phung khams kyi chos can rang bzhin
NK016(ma)005:2440: lhun grub dam tshig gi rdzas su dag pa la
NK016(ma)005:2441: spyi bo'i gtor ma ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin
NK016(ma)005:2442: bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye
NK016(ma)005:2443: shes dang ro mnyam pa chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du
NK016(ma)005:2444: babs nas ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i bdud rtsi'i mchod
NK016(ma)005:2445: sprin mkha' khyab tu spel bas /
NK016(ma)005:2446: 'khor 'das thams cad mchod yul du dag pa'i sku
NK016(ma)005:2447: gsung thugs kyi gsang ba rang bzhin dbyings kyi mkha'
NK016(ma)005:2448: 'gro mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo dang slob
NK016(ma)005:2449: ma'i lus ngag yid gsum ro gcig pa bde ba
NK016(ma)005:2450: chen por 'bar ba la sems 'dzin du bcug la
NK016(ma)005:2451: / cang te'u sogs rol mo'i sgra sbyar zhing /
NK016(ma)005:2452: sha chen gyi spos bsreg pa dang bcas pas 'khor
NK016(ma)005:2453: 'das thams cad dag pa rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK016(ma)005:2454: 'khor chen por yongs su sad par byas la /
NK016(ma)005:2455: bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan shar dang yi dam zhi khro'i sngags rnams brjod pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)005:2457: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma dam pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)005:2458: yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK016(ma)005:2461: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa dang bcas pa thams cad la /
NK016(ma)005:2462: slob bu'i lus longs spyod dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang
NK016(ma)005:2463: bcas pa thams cad srid zhi dbyer med kyi bdud
NK016(ma)005:2464: rtsi chen por sbyar zhing spel ba 'di 'bul zhing
NK016(ma)005:2465: mchis na gnyis su med par bzhes te gnas skabs
NK016(ma)005:2466: dang mthar thug gi phyi nang gsang ba'i bar chad
NK016(ma)005:2467: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2468: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK016(ma)005:2473: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa
NK016(ma)005:2474: rnams la zhes tha dad du phye na'ang legs par
NK016(ma)005:2475: 'gyur ro // de'i tshe lus 'phar zhing g.yo ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2476: ngag smra zhing dgod pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2477: sems rtog med 'od gsal gyi dbyings su grol ba'i nyams rnams byung rgyal du bskyang du gzhug /
NK016(ma)005:2478: gtor ma gnas su bzhag nas bla ma la spyi bos gtugs pa'i phyag bya yon dbul lo //
NK016(ma)005:2479: gsum pa kun tu bzang po rig pa rtsal gyi
NK016(ma)005:2480: dbang gis lhag pa'i ye shes ngo sprad pa la
NK016(ma)005:2481: gsum las / dang po rtags kun tu bzang po mtshon par byed pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2482: slob bus man+dala phul nas thal mo sbyar la /
NK016(ma)005:2484: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK016(ma)005:2485: rdo rje bla ma dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2486: yang dag don gyi mchog dam pa //
NK016(ma)005:2487: bdag la mngon du gyur par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2489: de nas slob bus stan bde ba la rnam snang gi chos bdun bcas la /
NK016(ma)005:2490: sems kyi rten snying gar kun tu bzang po mthing
NK016(ma)005:2491: ga mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil
NK016(ma)005:2492: mo krung gis bzhugs par bskyed la /
NK016(ma)005:2493: e h+ye his ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)005:2494: dzahmh'u bam hohs gnyis med du bstim la /
NK016(ma)005:2495: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gtad de /
NK016(ma)005:2496: 'di ni rang rig 'gyur ba med pa'i don ye shes lngar mtshon pa'i rtags yin no //
NK016(ma)005:2498: gnyis pa don kun tu bzang po ngo sprad pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2500: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK016(ma)005:2501: kun tu bzang pos ston par dka' //
NK016(ma)005:2503: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med //
NK016(ma)005:2504: rig pa sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK016(ma)005:2505: spros med rnam dag ye shes yin //
NK016(ma)005:2506: kun gzhi ye nas ma bcos pa //
NK016(ma)005:2507: bde chen rang shar klong du zhog /
NK016(ma)005:2508: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)005:2509: zhes pas sems skad cig ma gang skyes de ka rtsol bral bsal bzhag med par gzhag la /
NK016(ma)005:2510: sems kyi gshis gang du'ang ma grub pa mdangs bde chen du ma 'gag pa /
NK016(ma)005:2511: rtsal sna tshogs su snang ba /
NK016(ma)005:2512: bsgom bya sgom byed thams cad las 'das pa'i gsal
NK016(ma)005:2513: rig rjen ne ba spros pa dang bral ba de
NK016(ma)005:2514: ka ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin don kun tu bzang
NK016(ma)005:2515: po yin no // zhes ngo sprad /
NK016(ma)005:2516: gsum pa nyams kun tu bzang po bskyang du gzhug pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2518: snang stong dbyer med chos sku la //
NK016(ma)005:2519: rig stong bde ba chen por shar //
NK016(ma)005:2520: zung 'jug spros dang bral ba de //
NK016(ma)005:2521: kun tu bzang po'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)005:2522: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa
NK016(ma)005:2523: tu +aah zhes pas rjes shes gang shar gyi skye
NK016(ma)005:2524: 'gag gnas gsum gyi rang ngo la bltas pas rang
NK016(ma)005:2525: grol gyi ye shes gsal la mi rtog pa ni
NK016(ma)005:2526: nyams kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK016(ma)005:2528: sngar rjes mi bcad 'das pa'i 'du shes dor //
NK016(ma)005:2529: phyis sdun mi bsu yid kyi 'brel thag bcad //
NK016(ma)005:2530: bar du 'dzin med nam mkha'i ngang la bzhag /
NK016(ma)005:2531: ces pa ltar bskyang du gzhug go //
NK016(ma)005:2532: bzhi pa dam pa rigs brgya'i phyag rgya'i dbang gis
NK016(ma)005:2533: dag pa'i snang ba rab 'byams su bstan pa ni
NK016(ma)005:2534: / slob bu seng ges btegs pa'i khri la bcom
NK016(ma)005:2535: lngan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po yum dang bcas
NK016(ma)005:2536: pa'i rnam pas 'khod pa la dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK016(ma)005:2537: tshogs rnams mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul
NK016(ma)005:2538: du rim bzhin byon nas gnyis med du thim par
NK016(ma)005:2539: / bsam la / rgyas par na phyag gi bkol
NK016(ma)005:2540: byang las 'byung ba bzhin la 'don pa bsgyur ba'i
NK016(ma)005:2541: mthar so so'i sngags dang bcas pas re re bzhin
NK016(ma)005:2542: / bsam la / du bskur zhing / 'bring du
NK016(ma)005:2543: tshigs bcad kyis bsdus pa bzhin sde tshan du byas
NK016(ma)005:2544: / bsam la / du bskur zhing / nas dang
NK016(ma)005:2545: / shin tu bsdus pa ni bum pa gtso bo'i
NK016(ma)005:2546: phyag rgya dang bcas pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK016(ma)005:2547: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK016(ma)005:2548: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK016(ma)005:2549: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK016(ma)005:2550: zhi khro rab 'byams rgyal bas dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2553: badz+ri b+ha wa a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)005:2555: 'di ltar chos thams cad dam pa rigs brgya'i ngo bor dag cing /
NK016(ma)005:2556: de yang sems lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med gsang
NK016(ma)005:2557: chen rigs gcig tu rnam par dag pa yin no
NK016(ma)005:2560: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas sngags kyi phreng ba thon /
NK016(ma)005:2561: slob ma'i khar zhugs te snying gar thim par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2562: zhi khro'i spyi sngags dang yig brgya'i rjes zlos lan
NK016(ma)005:2563: gsum du byas nas sgom bzlas kyi dam bca' blang
NK016(ma)005:2564: / slob mas pan+dala phul te phyag btsal nas thal mo sbyar la /
NK016(ma)005:2565: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK016(ma)005:2566: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyid //
NK016(ma)005:2567: ces dam bcas te yon gyi dngos po ci 'byor pa dbul lo //
NK016(ma)005:2568: tshogs mchod kyi nang tshan bzhi pa tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK016(ma)005:2569: las kyi rdo rje phyag sngon du 'gro bas thabs shes rdzas rnams bsnol mar stob cing /
NK016(ma)005:2570: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK016(ma)005:2571: log rtog mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK016(ma)005:2572: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK016(ma)005:2573: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2575: des kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgya bskor zhing /
NK016(ma)005:2578: 'dus pa thams cad la brims te /
NK016(ma)005:2579: nang gi sbyin sreg gis rol pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)005:2580: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK016(ma)005:2581: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK016(ma)005:2582: ba ma lus pa dbang du 'du bar gyur cig
NK016(ma)005:2583: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2584: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang lang tsho la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2585: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK016(ma)005:2586: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK016(ma)005:2588: ces smon lam ga dab bo //
NK016(ma)005:2589: lnga pa lhag ma btang ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2590: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog med par bsdus pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2591: sngar gyi phud lhag bcas dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor dri'i man+dala gyi khar bzhag /
NK016(ma)005:2592: slob dpon gyi lce la rta mgrin yab yum rol
NK016(ma)005:2593: pa mdzad pa'i byang sems bdud rtsir phab par bsam
NK016(ma)005:2594: la / mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas dza gad kyi kha phru btab la /
NK016(ma)005:2595: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK016(ma)005:2596: purba bud+d+ha k+she tra p+aa la k+sho b+ha ka ra
NK016(ma)005:2597: h'u phata / ces pas byin brlab /
NK016(ma)005:2598: h'u las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:2599: mkha' 'gro lhag sdud ma sring ging gi tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:2600: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams //
NK016(ma)005:2601: dam tshig bzhin du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2602: e a ral+li hrim hrim dzahmh'u bam hohd+aa ki n+ai h'u dzah zhes bas spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)005:2603: h'u mkha' 'gro ging dang dbang phyug ma //
NK016(ma)005:2604: ma bdun sring bzhi 'bar ma brgyad //
NK016(ma)005:2605: pho nya la sogs lhag sdud tshogs //
NK016(ma)005:2606: dpal gyi pham phabs 'di gsol la //
NK016(ma)005:2607: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2608: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK016(ma)005:2610: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK016(ma)005:2611: dpal ldan nag mo re ma t+ai /
NK016(ma)005:2615: pho nya sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa rnams
NK016(ma)005:2616: kyi zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa
NK016(ma)005:2617: hi / ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:2618: ma h+aa ba li tam kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)005:2620: hoh lhag sdud gyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha'
NK016(ma)005:2621: 'gro dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)005:2622: rnams lhag ma'i dam tshig 'dis tshim zhing dgyes par
NK016(ma)005:2623: gyur te // dam tshig nyams chag thams cad skongs nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs /
NK016(ma)005:2625: dge 'dun dang chos kyi rgyal srid skyongs /
NK016(ma)005:2627: sems can gyi phan bde spel /
NK016(ma)005:2628: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi stong grogs mdzod /
NK016(ma)005:2629: sngags 'chang rnams kyi phrin las sgrubs /
NK016(ma)005:2630: khyad par dam tshig 'dir 'dus pa rnams kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i 'gal rkyen zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2631: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa myur du 'grub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)005:2634: zhes pas mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam la lhag ma dor zhing dkyil 'khor bsdu'o //
NK016(ma)005:2635: gsum pa brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2636: phyi rol du brtan ma'i gtor ma sman phud kyis bran la /
NK016(ma)005:2637: tram rat+na tree lo kya phata /
NK016(ma)005:2639: gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re zhing rin po
NK016(ma)005:2640: che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi shes pas nam
NK016(ma)005:2643: h'u tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK016(ma)005:2644: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK016(ma)005:2645: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK016(ma)005:2646: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2647: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK016(ma)005:2648: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK016(ma)005:2649: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK016(ma)005:2650: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK016(ma)005:2651: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK016(ma)005:2652: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK016(ma)005:2653: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK016(ma)005:2654: 'dir spyon dam skong phrin las mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2655: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK016(ma)005:2656: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK016(ma)005:2658: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng ge yes //
NK016(ma)005:2659: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK016(ma)005:2660: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK016(ma)005:2661: dbang bskur gsang ba'i mtshan nas ba rjod //
NK016(ma)005:2662: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK016(ma)005:2663: bod khams bsrung zhing skyong ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2664: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK016(ma)005:2665: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:2666: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs pa //
NK016(ma)005:2667: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK016(ma)005:2668: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK016(ma)005:2674: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u h'u /
NK016(ma)005:2676: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs sman raka gtor gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK016(ma)005:2678: brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis
NK016(ma)005:2679: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs kyis phrin las
NK016(ma)005:2680: bcol nas / ya hi gats+tsha gshegs su gsol nas gtor ma gtsang sar skyel lo //
NK016(ma)005:2681: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2682: gtang rag gi mchod pa bshams shing byin gyis brlabs te /
NK016(ma)005:2686: sman gtor rak+ta bcas pas mchod cing bstod nas /
NK016(ma)005:2688: yi dam zhi khro rigs gcig dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)005:2689: sgrub rdzas dman zhing ting 'dzin cho ga nyams //
NK016(ma)005:2690: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa ci mchis bzod par gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2691: tshangs pa mchog gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2693: yi ge brgya pa bzlas pas bzod gsol byas la /
NK016(ma)005:2695: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK016(ma)005:2696: ji srid nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can
NK016(ma)005:2697: thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'da' ba'i
NK016(ma)005:2698: sa la ma bzhag gi bar du rgyal ba rnams
NK016(ma)005:2699: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar brtan par bzhugs su
NK016(ma)005:2700: gsol / khyad par du'ang ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)005:2701: 'di nyid la ji srid 'byung ba bzhi'i gnod pas
NK016(ma)005:2702: ma zhig gi bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK016(ma)005:2703: gsol / / brtan par bzhugs nas bdag dang sems
NK016(ma)005:2704: can thams cad la mchog dang thun mong gi dngos
NK016(ma)005:2705: grub ma lus pa rtsal du gsol /
NK016(ma)005:2706: su pra tish+tha badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)005:2707: zhes pas brtan bzhugs byas la /
NK016(ma)005:2708: b+h+r+au bi shwa bi shud+d+he h'u s+w+aa h+aa h'u ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK016(ma)005:2709: zhes pas dam tshig gi 'khor lo gsal btab la /
NK016(ma)005:2710: badz+ra pad+ma sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)005:2711: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)005:2712: a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)005:2713: dzahmh'u bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK016(ma)005:2714: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros pas
NK016(ma)005:2715: snod bcud thams cad dag cing 'od gsal bar byas
NK016(ma)005:2717: dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang la thim /
NK016(ma)005:2719: 'khor rnams rim bzhin gtso bo yab yum la /
NK016(ma)005:2721: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)005:2724: h'u gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK016(ma)005:2725: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK016(ma)005:2728: zhes pas thun mtshams kyi lhar langs te /
NK016(ma)005:2729: snang grags rig gsum lha sngags chos nyid kyi rang bzhin du shes par byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:2732: mgrin par +aah snying gar h'u yig rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK016(ma)005:2733: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK016(ma)005:2735: lus rdo rje'i go chas zhu lugs su g.yogs pas
NK016(ma)005:2736: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer mi phyed par
NK016(ma)005:2737: bsam zhing / thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)005:2738: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK016(ma)005:2739: ces brjod cing nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:2740: rdul tshon gyi cho ga zhag sbrel du byed pa'i nyin snga ma rnams la'ang de kho na dang /
NK016(ma)005:2744: ye shes kyi 'khor lo nam mkhar btegs nas /
NK016(ma)005:2745: gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang bzod gsol byas nas //
NK016(ma)005:2746: khyod kyis sems can don kun badzada //
NK016(ma)005:2748: dz+ny+aa na man+da la badz+ra muh zhes pas gshegs su gsol la /
NK016(ma)005:2749: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bsdu tshul sngar bzhin byas nas /
NK016(ma)005:2750: dus de nyid dam nangs par lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas /
NK016(ma)005:2751: a k+aa ro bzla zhing rdo rje dang bcas pa'i
NK016(ma)005:2752: lag gis thog mar lha mtshan rnams bsdus la cung
NK016(ma)005:2754: de nas dbang ldan nas brtsams te gtso bo'i gnas
NK016(ma)005:2755: kyi bar rim gyis phyags la cung zad gzhan la'ang
NK016(ma)005:2756: sbyin / lhag ma rnams snod bzang por blugs nas
NK016(ma)005:2757: mchod pa dang bkur sti chen pos chu klung du
NK016(ma)005:2758: sbyin / dor / bum chu lhag ma la sogs pas kyang gzhan la phan par bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:2759: lnga pa bsngo ba shis brjod bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)005:2760: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)005:2761: deng 'dir brtson pas bsgrubs pa'i dge ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2762: dus gsum bsags dang yod pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK016(ma)005:2763: bsdoms te bla med byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK016(ma)005:2764: deng nas byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK016(ma)005:2765: rigs bzang blo gsal nga rgyal med pa dang //
NK016(ma)005:2766: snying rje che zhing bla ma la gus ldan //
NK016(ma)005:2767: dpal ldan rdo rje'i theg la nges gnas shog /
NK016(ma)005:2768: dbang gis smiin cing dam tshig sdom par ldan //
NK016(ma)005:2769: rim gnyis lam la bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin te //
NK016(ma)005:2770: dka' ba med par rig 'dzin go 'phang bgrod //
NK016(ma)005:2771: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2772: cir snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lor rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:2773: grags pa thams cad brjod bral sngags kyi sgra //
NK016(ma)005:2774: sems kyi 'gyu ba rang rig 'dus ma byas //
NK016(ma)005:2775: bde chen 'du 'bral med ba mngon gyur shog /
NK016(ma)005:2776: nyams chag rtog sgrib ma spangs gnas su dag /
NK016(ma)005:2777: phyi nang gsang ba dbyer med rtogs pas skongs //
NK016(ma)005:2778: gang shar rang grol kun bzang klong yangs su //
NK016(ma)005:2779: ngan song dong sprugs srid zhi mnyam gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2780: thig le chen por sku dang zhing khams rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:2781: dam tshig chen por spang blang mtshan ma dag /
NK016(ma)005:2782: khyab brdal chen por re dogs mdud pa grol //
NK016(ma)005:2783: rdzogs pa chen por chos sku mngon gyur shog /
NK016(ma)005:2784: brgyud pa gsum gyi byin rlabs snying la zhugs //
NK016(ma)005:2785: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam gsang sems la rdzogs //
NK016(ma)005:2786: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK016(ma)005:2787: mu mtha' med pa'i 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK016(ma)005:2788: zhi khro sprul pa'i 'khor los lung ston cing //
NK016(ma)005:2789: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bu bzhin skyong ba dang //
NK016(ma)005:2790: chos skyong srung mas bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK016(ma)005:2791: yid la smon pa mtha' dag 'grub gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2792: rgyal ba'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK016(ma)005:2793: bstan 'dzin rnams kyi bzhed pa'i don kun grub //
NK016(ma)005:2794: ma lus skye rgu'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi zhing //
NK016(ma)005:2795: phun tshogs mtha' dag yid bzhin 'byor gyur cig /
NK016(ma)005:2798: dga' ston bya ba sogs mtha' rgyas kyi cho ga rnams gsang ba spyi'i 'gros bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK016(ma)005:2799: cho ga 'di la rgyud dang man ngag gi gzhung
NK016(ma)005:2800: so so la brten pa'i lugs srol tha dad 'ga'
NK016(ma)005:2801: zhig mchis te / rang gzhung tshugs pa'i dbang du byas pa gsum dang /
NK016(ma)005:2802: dkyil 'khor gzhan la sbyar ba ste bzhi las /
NK016(ma)005:2806: bzhi ba gzhan la sbyar ba'o //
NK016(ma)005:2808: glang po che rab 'bogs kyi rtog pa gcig khol
NK016(ma)005:2809: du phyungs pa dri med bshags pa'i rgyud nyid kyi
NK016(ma)005:2810: don gu rus mdzad pa'i gdams ngag gi las tho
NK016(ma)005:2813: bshags rgyud du zhi khro'i le'u gsungs tshul gyi go rim bzhin sgrub pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2815: yi ge brgya ba dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud la brten pa ste gzhan du bshad pa ltar dang /
NK016(ma)005:2818: yang dag zhi khro sogs bkol rgyud 'dis kha skong ba ste /
NK016(ma)005:2819: de dag kyang bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis 'ching ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2820: gleng gzhi bdun gyis mching ba sogs lugs tha dad par grags kyang /
NK016(ma)005:2821: don gyi gnad gcig tu 'bab pa lta bur yod cing /
NK016(ma)005:2822: dbang bka' dang byin rlabs kyi rgyun yang chad med du yod bzhin pa yin kyang /
NK016(ma)005:2823: 'dir bkod de thams cad las kyang phul du byung ba'i ngo mtshar dang ldan pa yin te /
NK016(ma)005:2824: gang la brten bya'i rgyud kyi dngos su bstan pa'i don la 'byor zhing ma 'khrugs pa dang /
NK016(ma)005:2825: de'i gsal byed slob dpon gyis mdzad pa'i man ngag
NK016(ma)005:2826: sum cu rtsa drug pa'i nang tshan man ngag nyer
NK016(ma)005:2827: bzhi pa sogs rgya bod kyi gzhung rnying khungs tshad
NK016(ma)005:2828: du mas gsal por bkral ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2829: dpal sangs rgyas gsang ba'i man ngag bi ma la
NK016(ma)005:2830: dang gnyags lo nas brgyud pa'i bka' srol nyams pa
NK016(ma)005:2831: med pa'i dngos bstan nyid de /
NK016(ma)005:2834: g.yung ston chen po sogs tshad mar grub pa'i sngags
NK016(ma)005:2835: 'chang chen po brgyud mar byon pa rnams kyi phyag
NK016(ma)005:2836: bzhes kyi gtso bo yang 'di la mdzad pa dang
NK016(ma)005:2837: / brgyud pa'i khyad par du ma'i dbang gi bka'
NK016(ma)005:2838: ma chad pa'i byin rlabs kyi chu bo'i rgyun yang
NK016(ma)005:2840: cho ga'i khrigs bkod kyang tshig don ma 'dzings shing rnam par gsal ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2841: lag len gyi 'jug pa bde ba sogs khyad par du gyur pa yin mod kyi /
NK016(ma)005:2842: 'on kyang las khrigs gzhung rnying rnams ni ha cang bsdus shing mi gsal ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2843: bar skabs su byon pa'i mkhas pa dag gis mdzad
NK016(ma)005:2844: pa yang lugs srol tha dad pa'i nang gses cung
NK016(ma)005:2845: zad 'dres pa ltar snang ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2846: 'ga' zhig ni ha cang rgyas ches pa dang yig
NK016(ma)005:2847: sna mang du bsdus pas snying po'i don la sgrib
NK016(ma)005:2848: pa sogs dus mtha'i 'gro ba la phan pa che
NK016(ma)005:2850: 'dir bkod gang la brten bya'i khungs dang 'byor zhing snying po'i don tshang la 'dril ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2851: kha skong bar 'os pa rnams kyang cho ga nang
NK016(ma)005:2852: mthun pa rnams kyis don thob ji ltar yod pa
NK016(ma)005:2853: bzhin bskangs nas bklag chog gtsang dag tu byas pa
NK016(ma)005:2854: yin la / spyir 'di nyid yo ga rnam pa
NK016(ma)005:2855: gsum ka dang 'brel ba'i gsang ba spyi'i cho ga
NK016(ma)005:2857: khyad par lung a nu yo ga'i nang tshan du gnas pa ste /
NK016(ma)005:2858: go don dang lag len gyi zur 'debs phyogs mthong tsam zhig 'chad par yang 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)005:2859: na rag dong sprugs rnal 'byor spyi khrus kyi //
NK016(ma)005:2860: rnam dag cho ga'i sgrub thabs zla med pas //
NK016(ma)005:2861: 'jigs rung 'khor ba'i mtsho las 'gro ba kun //
NK016(ma)005:2862: thar mchog zhing du sgrol byed 'di kho na //
NK016(ma)005:2863: srid mtsho brgal ba'i thabs las gzhan gyur pa'i //
NK016(ma)005:2864: 'dod don bsgrub bya thar 'dod rnams la med //
NK016(ma)005:2865: de phyir rnam dag myur ba'i lam bzang gi //
NK016(ma)005:2866: thabs tshul 'di la kun tu 'bad pa gces //
NK016(ma)005:2867: rgyud don man ngag lag len ldan pa'i khrigs //
NK016(ma)005:2868: phyogs tsam brjod pa'i dge ba gang thob des //
NK016(ma)005:2869: 'gro kun srid zhi'i mtha' las rnam grol ba'i //
NK016(ma)005:2870: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang 'thob phyir ba sngo //
NK016(ma)005:2871: na rag dong sprugs rnal 'byor gyi spyi khrus chen
NK016(ma)005:2872: po'i cho ga 'khor ba kun sgrol zhes bya ba
NK016(ma)005:2873: 'di ni / rtse le chos rje mthu stobs rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK016(ma)005:2874: mdo khams go 'jo ba sdom brtson shes rab 'od
NK016(ma)005:2875: zer sogs don gnyer can du mas snga phyir nan
NK016(ma)005:2877: rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes rang lo
NK016(ma)005:2878: zhe dgu pa la o rgyan smin grol gling gi
NK016(ma)005:2879: dge gnas su sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni mkhan
